Taylor%20and%20had%20moved%20out%20with%20their%20son.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20former%C2%A0%26quot%3BVanderpump%20Rules%26quot%3B%20stars%20returned%20to%20reality%20TV%20for%20their%20spinoff%C2%A0%26quot%3BThe%20Valley.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ECartwright%20and%20Taylor%20married%20in%202019%20after%20surviving%20a%20cheating%20scandal%20on%C2%A0%26quot%3BVanderpump%20Rules.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fvanderpump-rules-jax-taylor-and-brittany-cartwright-relationship-timeline-2019-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBrittany%20Cartwright%20and%20Jax%20Taylor's%20famously%20tumultuous%20relationship%3C%2Fa%3E%20might%20be%20over%20for%20good.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20former%20%26quot%3BVanderpump%20Rules%26quot%3B%20stars%2C%20who%20first%20started%20dating%20in%202015%20after%20meeting%20in%20Las%20Vegas%2C%20recently%20announced%20they'd%20separated%20after%20four%20years%20of%20marriage.%20The%20announcement%20came%20just%20weeks%20before%20the%20premiere%20of%20%26quot%3BThe%20Valley%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20new%20spinoff%20show%20starring%20Taylor%2C%20Cartwright%2C%20and%20fellow%20former%20%26quot%3BVPR%26quot%3B%20star%20Kristen%20Doute.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BJax%20and%20I%20are%20taking%20time%20apart%20and%20I%20made%20the%20decision%20to%20move%20into%20another%20home%20to%20take%20some%20space%20for%20the%20sake%20of%20my%20mental%20health%2C%26quot%3B%20Cartwright%20said%20on%20the%20February%2029%20episode%20of%20their%20joint%20podcast%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.iheart.com%2Fpodcast%2F586-when-reality-hits-with-jax-112236371%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20Reality%20Hits.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere's%20what%20we%20know%20about%20Cartwright%20and%20Taylor's%20break-up%20and%20what%20they've%20said%20about%20the%20possibility%20of%20reconciling.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EWhy%20did%20Brittany%20Cartwright%20and%20Jax%20Taylor%20split%3F%3