penAI%20investor%20Microsoft's%20latest%20move%20in%20the%20fight%20for%20artificial%20intelligence%20supremacy.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ELike%20many%20Big%20Tech%20names%2C%20Microsoft%20has%20been%20battling%20for%20supremacy%20in%20the%20fast-evolving%20AI%20field.%20Its%20latest%20move%3A%20hiring%20Mustafa%20Suleyman%2C%20a%20key%20figure%20in%20the%20field%20thanks%20to%20cofounding%20DeepMind%20%E2%80%94%20now%20competitor%20Google's%20AI%20division.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linkedin.com%2Fin%2Fmustafa-suleyman%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esocial%20media%20posts%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20Suleyman%20said%20he's%20taking%20on%20the%20role%20of%20%3Cspan%3ECEO%20of%20Microsoft%20AI%2C%20leading%20all%20consumer%20AI%20products%20and%20research%2C%20including%20Copilot%2C%20Bing%2C%20and%20Edge.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2F2024-03-19%2Fmicrosoft-hires-deepmind-co-founder-suleyman-to-run-consumer-ai%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBloomberg%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Suleyman%20will%20report%20directly%20to%20Microsoft%20CEO%20Satya%20Nadella.%20It's%20the%20first%20time%20one%20leader%20will%20oversee%20Microsoft's%20consumer%20AI%20products.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20want%20to%20make%20sure%20that%20this%20next%20wave%20is%20one%20that%20for%20the%20consumer%20Microsoft%20can%20really%2C%20really%20create%20incredible%20products%2C%26quot%3B%20Suleyman%20told%20Bloomberg.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMicrosoft's%20hire%20of%20the%20well-known%20AI%20leader%20appears%20to%20be%20part%20of%20an%20effort%20to%20bolster%20its%20strategy%20outside%20its%20ongoing%20partnership%20with%20OpenAI.%20Last%20January%2C%20Microsoft%20announced%20it%20was%20pumping%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmicrosoft-talks-invest-billions-openai-chatgpt-owner-report-2023-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%2410%20billion%20into%20the%20ChatGPT%20maker%20%3C%2Fa%3Eto%20create%20the%20best%20AI%20products.%20It%20also%20tried%2C%20albeit%20unsuccessfully%2C%20to%20hire%20OpenAI%20CEO%20Sam%20Altman%20in%20November%20last%20year%20after%20he%20was%20briefly%20ousted%20from%20the%20company.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20move%20steps%20up%20its%20competition%20with%20Google%2C%20which%20Suleyman%20left%20in%202022.%20The%20Alphabet%20division%20has%20been%20pushing%20ahead%20in%20AI%20%E2%80%94%20despite%20some%20snafus.%20Gemini%2C%20Google's%20rival%20to%20ChatGPT%2C%20has%20come%20under%20attack%20after%20people%20complained%20its%20image%20generation%20feature%20produced%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-gemini-ai-pause-image-generation-people-woke-complaints-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehistorically%20inaccurate%20photos%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20US%20presidents.%20Still%2C%20Google%20grabbed%20headlines%20this%20week%20after%20Bloomberg%20reported%20it's%20in%20talks%20with%20Apple%20to%20integrate%20%3Cspan%3EGemini%20into%20the%20iPhone.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20leaving%20Google%2C%20Suleyman%20has%20been%20running%20his%20startup%2C%20Inflection%20AI%2C%20since%20February%202022.%20Kar%C3%A9n%20Simonyan%2C%20Inflection's%20cofounder%2C%20will%20join%20Microsoft's%20AI%20division%20as%20Chief%20Scientist%2C%20Suleyman%20said%2C%20and%20several%20teammates%20he%20didn't%20name%20will%20also%20join.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInflection%20will%20now%20stop%20running%20its%20AI%20chatbot%2C%20Pi%20%E2%80%94%20a%20smaller%20rival%20to%20ChatGPT%20%E2%80%94%20and%20%3Cspan%3Einstead%20sell%20AI%20software%20to%20businesses%2C%20Bloomberg%20reported.%20%3C%2Fspan%3EMicrosoft%20told%20Bloomberg%20it%20will%20continue%20to%20provide%20Inflection%20with%20compute%20power%20to%20build%20its%20AI%20models%2C%20which%20the%20software%20giant%20noted%20will%20be%20part%20of%20its%20software.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMicrosoft%20and%20Inflection%20AI%20didn't%20imm