%20Naveen%20Patnaik's%20Aide%20Amid%20BJP-BJD%20Alliance%20Buzz%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20and%20BJD%20do%20not%20need%20each%20other%20to%20win%20elections%2C%20but%20some%20things%20are%20beyond%20politics%20and%20the%20two%20leaders%20--%20PM%20Narendra%20Modi%20and%20CM%20Naveen%20Patnaik%20--%20want%20to%20come%20together%20for%20%26quot%3Ba%20greater%20cause%26quot%3B%2C%20said%20VK%20Pandian%2C%20the%20close%20aide%20of%20the%20chief%20minister.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20at%20a%20media%20conclave%20in%20New%20Delhi%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20he%20said%20Chief%20Minister%20Patnaik%20and%20PM%20Modi%20share%20a%20great%20friendship.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSomebody%20wants%20to%20join%20an%20alliance%20because%20they%20want%20to%20have%20an%20impact%20on%20the%20electoral%20map.%20Here%20is%20a%20chief%20minister%20who%20is%20so%20popular%20in%20the%20state%20and%20he%20gets%203%2F4th%20majority%20every%20time.%20In%20the%20recently%20concluded%20panchayat%20elections%2C%20which%20are%20fought%20on%20party%20symbols%2C%20he%20got%2090%20per%20cent%20of%20the%20seats.%20The%20second%20party%20is%20the%20BJP%20with%205%20per%20cent%20of%20seats.%20So%2C%20Mr%20Naveen%20Patnaik%20does%20not%20need%20an%20alliance%20to%20come%20back%20to%20serve%20the%20people.%20I%20would%20say%20the%20same%20thing%20about%20Mr%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20the%20honourable%20PM%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Pandian%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B...there%20are%20some%20things%20beyond%20politics.%20It%20is%20a%20mark%20of%20great%20statesmanship%2C%20that's%20how%20I%20put%20it.%20Two%20great%20leaders%20wanting%20to%20come%20together%20for%20a%20greater%20cause.%20It%20has%20significance%20as%20two%20great%20people%20coming%20together%20as%20a%20mark%20of%20statesmanship.%20That's%20how%20I%20see%20it%2C%20and%20even%20the%20chief%20minister%20thinks%20that%20way.%20It%20has%20no%20electoral%20value%20either%20for%20the%20BJD%20or%20the%20BJP%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Pandian%20said%20the%20PM%20and%20the%20chief%20minister%20see%20some%20things%20that%20are%20beyond%20politics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBJD%20does%20not%20need%20BJP%20to%20form%20government%20in%20the%20state%2C%20and%20BJP%20may%20not%20need%20BJD%20to%20form%20government%20at%20the%20Centre.%20That's%20why%20I%20made%20it%20very%20clear%20that%20it%20has%20to%20do%20with%20two%20individuals%20who%20share%20a%20great%20friendship%20and%20they%20see%20some%20things%20are%20beyond%20politics.%20A%20rare%20mark%20of%20statesmanship%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20about%20the%20status%20of%20the%20alliance%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BIf%20anything%20happens%2C%20we%20will%20all%20get%20to%20know...%20I%20told%20the%20logic%20behind%20this%20whatever%20talk%20(over%20the%20alliance)%20has%20happened.%26quot%3B%20Pandian's%20statement%20comes%20amid%20weeks%20of%20speculations%20about%20an%20alliance%20between%20the%20state's%20ruling%20party%20and%20the%20main%20opposition%2C%20ahead%20of%20the%20simultaneous%20elections%20to%2021%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%20in%20the%20state%20and%20the%20147-member%20assembly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20state%20BJP%20leaders%20rejected%20the%20speculations%20on%20several%20occasions%2C%20asserting%20that%20they%20would%20fight%20the%20elections%20on%20their%20own%20and%20oust%20the%20BJD%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20and%20BJD%20were%20in%20alliance%20for%2011%20years%2C%20from%201998%20to%202009.%20Over%20the%20last%20decade%2C%20the%20BJP%20decimated%20the%20Congress%20to%20emerge%20as%20the%20main%20opposition%20party%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20BJD%20often%20extended%20support%20to%20the%20BJP%20in%20Parliament%20on%20crucial%20legislations%20and%20even%20helped%20Railway%20Minister%20Ashwini%20Vaishnaw%20get%20elected%20to%20Rajya%20Sabha%20from%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%202019%20elections%2C%20BJD%20won%201