n-patnaiks-aide-amid-bjp-bjd-alliance-buzz-5269847%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fno-electoral-value-naveen-patnaiks-aide-amid-bjp-bjd-alliance-buzz-5269847%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Discontent%20In%20Karnataka%20BJP%20After%201st%20List%20Of%20Lok%20Sabha%20Polls'%20Candidates%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP's%20first%20list%20of%2020%20candidates%20for%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20in%20Karnataka%20has%20caused%20discontent%20among%20leaders%20in%20the%20state%20with%20few%20claiming%20that%20they%20would%20switch%20over%20to%20Congress.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFormer%20Deputy%20Chief%20Minister%20K%20S%20Eshwarappa%2C%20a%20staunch%20RSS%20supporter%2C%20has%20revolted%20against%20the%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEshwarappa%20went%20all%20out%20against%20the%20former%20chief%20minister%20and%20BJP%20parliamentary%20board%20member%20B%20S%20Yediyurappa%20after%20his%20son%20K%20E%20Kantesh%20could%20not%20make%20it%20to%20the%20list%20of%20candidates%20announced%20by%20the%20high%20command%20a%20week%20ago.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKarnataka%20has%2028%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20leader%20wanted%20a%20ticket%20for%20his%20son%20from%20the%20Haveri%20Lok%20Sabha%20seat%2C%20but%20the%20party%20fielded%20the%20sitting%20MLA%20and%20former%20Chief%20Minister%20Basavaraj%20Bommai%20from%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUpset%20over%20the%20development%2C%20Eshwarappa%20announced%20that%20he%20would%20contest%20the%20elections%20from%20Shivamogga%20against%20Yediyurappa's%20elder%20son%20B%20Y%20Vijayendra%20as%20a%20mark%20of%20protest%20against%20'dynastic%20politics%20in%20Karnataka'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20interview%20with%20PTI%2C%20Eshwarappa%20alleged%20that%20the%20BJP%20is%20in%20bad%20shape%20in%20Karnataka.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPeople%20and%20the%20workers%20are%20in%20favour%20of%20the%20BJP%20but%20the%20system%20here%20is%20bad.%20What%20is%20our%20Narendra%20Modi%20ji%20saying%3F%20The%20Congress%20party%20is%20in%20the%20hands%20of%20one%20family.%20Rahul%20Gandhi%2C%20Sonia%20Gandhi...%20the%20central%20Congress%20is%20being%20controlled%20by%20one%20family.%20Same%20situation%20in%20Karnataka.%20Karnataka's%20BJP%20is%20in%20control%20of%20one%20family.%20We%20have%20to%20protest%20this%2C%26quot%3B%20the%2075-year-old%20leader%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20even%20charged%20that%20those%20standing%20in%20favour%20of%20Hindutva%20are%20being%20sidelined%2C%20be%20it%20C%20T%20Ravi%2C%20Pratap%20Simha%2C%20Basanagouda%20Patil%20Yatnal%20or%20Sadananda%20Gowda.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BUnder%20any%20circumstances%2C%20I%20will%20have%20to%20fight%20the%20election%2C%20which%20I%20will%20do%2C%26quot%3B%20Eshwarappa%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFormer%20Chief%20Minister%20D%20V%20Sadananda%20Gowda%20who%20was%20initially%20reluctant%20to%20contest%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%2C%20has%20suddenly%20expressed%20his%20strong%20desire%20to%20fight%20the%20polls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Tuesday%20he%20even%20hinted%20that%20he%20might%20consider%20joining%20Congress%20and%20make%20his%20decision%20public%20in%20a%20press%20conference%20on%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Koppal%2C%20two-time%20BJP%20MLA%20Karadi%20Sanganna%20is%20upset%20over%20being%20denied%20a%20ticket.%20The%20party%20has%20decided%20to%20field%20Dr%20Basavaraj%20Kyavator.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20angry%20Sanganna%20said%20he%20too%20is%20in%20touch%20with%20Congress%20leaders%20%26quot%3Bbut%20no%20decision%20has%20been%20taken%20yet%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20will%20not%20decide%20now.%20We%20have%20a%20meeting%20with%20our%20party%20leaders%20on%20Thursday.%20I%20will%20go%20with%20whatever%20our%20leaders%20will%20suggest%20whether%20to%20stay%20in%20the%20party%20or%20join%20Congress%2C%26quot%3B%20Sanganna%20told%20reporters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20has%20fielded%20V%20Somanna%20from%20Tumakuru%2C%20which%20has%