1901108_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22No%20Voting%20Arrangement%20So%20Far%20For%20Those%20Displaced%20In%20Manipur%3A%20Official%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThousands%20of%20Kuki-Zo%20community%20people%20of%20Manipur%2C%20who%20have%20taken%20shelter%20in%20Mizoram%20following%20the%20ethnic%20violence%20in%20their%20home%20state%2C%20may%20not%20be%20able%20to%20exercise%20their%20franchise%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%2C%20an%20official%20said%20on%20Tuesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENo%20voting%20arrangement%20has%20been%20made%20for%20these%20Internally%20Displaced%20People%20(IDPs)%20from%20Manipur%20till%20now%2C%20an%20Election%20Commission%20official%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Mizoram%20Home%20Department's%20data%20accessed%20by%20PTI%2C%20altogether%209%2C196%20adults%20and%20children%20from%20neighbouring%20Manipur%20have%20taken%20shelter%20in%20different%20parts%20of%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20discussion%20is%20on%20among%20officials%20of%20the%20Election%20Commission%20to%20enable%20the%20Manipuris%2C%20displaced%20in%20different%20parts%20of%20the%20country%2C%20to%20exercise%20their%20franchise%20in%20the%20upcoming%20polls.%20However%2C%20till%20now%2C%20there%20is%20no%20plan%20to%20make%20special%20arrangements%20for%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20official%20told%20PTI%20on%20condition%20of%20anonymity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20two%20Manipur%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%20will%20go%20to%20polls%20on%20April%2019.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChief%20Election%20Commissioner%20Rajiv%20Kumar%20recently%20said%20that%20the%20EC%20has%20drawn%20up%20a%20scheme%20to%20allow%20displaced%20people%20in%20Manipur%20to%20cast%20their%20votes%20from%20the%20camps%20where%20they%20are%20staying.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EManipur's%20Chief%20Electoral%20Officer%20(CEO)%20Pradeep%20Kumar%20Jha%20had%20told%20reporters%20that%20the%20scheme%20is%20limited%20to%20the%20state's%20territorial%20jurisdiction.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to