seless%20arguments%20in%20this%20regard%20does%20not%20lend%20such%20claims%20any%20validity%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%20on%20Tuesday%20(March%2019).%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EJaiswal%20added%3A%20%E2%80%9CArunachal%20Pradesh%20was%2C%20is%20and%20will%20always%20be%20an%20integral%20and%20inalienable%20part%20of%20India.%20Its%20people%20will%20continue%20to%20benefit%20from%20our%20development%20programmes%20and%20infrastructure%20projects.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Chinese%20side%20had%20also%20claimed%20that%20the%20current%20situation%20at%20the%20border%20was%20%E2%80%9Cstable%E2%80%9D%20but%20that%20Indian%20actions%20were%20%E2%80%9Ccontrary%20to%20the%20efforts%20of%20both%20sides%20to%20ease%20the%20border%20situation%20and%20are%20not%20conducive%20to%20maintaining%20peace%20and%20tranquility%20in%20the%20border%20areas%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CCurrently%2C%20the%20overall%20situation%20in%20the%20China-India%20border%20areas%20is%20stable%2C%20and%20both%20sides%20maintain%20effective%20communication%20through%20diplomatic%20and%20military%20channels%20to%20address%20border%20issues%20of%20mutual%20concern%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20the%20Chinese%20spokesperson.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20has%20been%20no%20official%20comment%20from%20the%20Indian%20side%20on%20media%20reports%20that%20India%20was%20deploying%2010%2C000%20soldiers%20to%20the%20India-China%20border.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710869976000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F19230821%2FAP.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Findia-again-reiterates-sovereignty-over-arunachal-after-latest-verbal-barb-from-china%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%E2%80%9CRepeating%20baseless%20arguments%20in%20this%20regard%20does%20not%20lend%20such%20claims%20any%20validity%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20external%20affairs%20mini