0from%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20in%20December%20last%20year%20for%20%26quot%3Bunethical%20conduct%26quot%3B%20and%20has%20moved%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20challenging%20her%20expulsion.%20She%20has%20been%20renominated%20by%20the%20party%20as%20its%20candidate%20from%20the%20Krishnanagar%20Lok%20Sabha%20seat%20in%20West%20Bengal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Lokpal%20directive%20came%20while%20deciding%20a%20complaint%20by%20BJP%20Lok%20Sabha%20member%20Nishikant%20Dubey%20alleging%20that%20Moitra%20had%20asked%20questions%20in%20the%20Lower%20House%20of%20Parliament%20in%20exchange%20for%20cash%20and%20gifts%20from%20Dubai-based%20businessman%20Darshan%20Hiranandani.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAfter%20careful%20evaluation%20and%20consideration%20of%20the%20entire%20material%20on%20record%2C%20there%20remains%20no%20doubt%20regarding%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20allegations%20levelled%20against%20the%20RPS%20(Respondent%20Public%20Servant)%2C%20most%20of%20which%20are%20supported%20by%20cogent%20evidence%2C%20are%20extremely%20serious%20in%20nature%2C%20especially%20in%20view%20of%20the%20position%20held%20by%20her%2C%26quot%3B%20reads%20the%20Lokpal%20order.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20has%20referred%20to%20Ms%20Moitra%20as%20the%20RPS%20in%20the%20order.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTherefore%2C%20in%20our%20considered%20opinion%2C%20a%20deeper%20probe%20is%20required%20to%20establish%20the%20truth.%20This%20is%20vital%20in%20view%20of%20the%20position%20and%20status%20held%20by%20the%20RPS%20at%20the%20relevant%20point%20of%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20order%20of%20the%20Lokpal%20bench%20comprising%20Justice%20Abhilasha%20Kumari%20(judicial%20member)%20and%20Members%20Archana%20Ramasundaram%20and%20Mahender%20Singh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20said%20whatever%20be%20the%20position%20held%2C%20a%20public%20servant%20is%20bound%20to%20exercise%20probity%20in%20the%20discharge%20of%20his%20or%20her%20duties.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20responsibility%20and%20burden%20are%20heavier%20on%20the%20shoulders%20of%20a%20public%20representative.%20Corruption%20is%20a%20malaise%20that%20is%20adversely%20affecting%20the%20legislative%2C%20administrative%2C%20social%20and%20economic%20functioning%20of%20this%20democratic%20country%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20order%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20a%20duty%20cast%20upon%20us%20and%2C%20indeed%2C%20the%20mandate%20of%20the%20(Lokpal)%20Act%2C%20that%20all%20attempts%20be%20made%20to%20root%20out%20corruption%20and%20corrupt%20practises%20that%20bring%20under%20their%20fold%20aspects%20such%20as%20undue%20advantage%2C%20illegal%20gain%20or%20benefit%20and%20quid%20pro%20quo%20in%20the%20discharge%20of%20public%20duties%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccordingly%2C%20%26quot%3Bwe%20direct%20the%20CBI...to%20investigate%20all%20aspects%20of%20the%20allegations%20made%20in%20the%20complaint%2C%20and%20submit%20a%20copy%20of%20the%20investigation%20report%20within%20a%20period%20of%20six%20months%20from%20the%20date%20of%20receipt%20of%20this%20order%26quot%3B%2C%20the%20order%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CBI%20shall%20also%20file%20periodical%20reports%20regarding%20the%20status%20of%20the%20investigation%2C%20every%20month%2C%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710869220000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2F8vbk0nb_mahua-moitra-image-test_625x300_12_December_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flokpal-asks-cbi-to-probe-cash-for-query-allegation-against-trinamools-mahua-moitra-5271123%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Anti-corruption%20ombudsman%20Lokpal%20on%20Tuesday%20directed%20the%20CBI%20to%20investigate%20the%20cash-for-query%20allegations%20against%20Trinamool%20Congress%20(TMC)%20leader%20Mahua%20Moitra%20