-melbourne-to-bali-forced-to-turn-back-after-passenger-bangs-on-cockpit-door-5270553%5C%22%3EFlight%20From%20Melbourne%20To%20Bali%20Forced%20To%20Turn%20Back%20After%20Passenger%20Bangs%20On%20Cockpit%20Door%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAn%20investigation%20conducted%20by%20CPD's%20Homicide%20Unit%20revealed%20that%20Candelario%20left%20her%20child%20alone%20and%20unattended%20from%20June%206%20to%20June%2016%20to%20vacation%20in%20Detroit%2C%20Michigan%2C%20and%20in%20Puerto%20Rico.%20Jailyn%20was%20extremely%20dehydrated%20at%20the%20time%20of%20death%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20office%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BJailyn%20was%20discovered%20in%20a%20Pack-N-Play%20pen%20on%20a%20liner%20soiled%20with%20urine%20and%20feces%20with%20soiled%20blankets%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20statement%20read.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20mother%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20claims%20to%20have%20struggled%20with%20depression%20and%20other%20mental%20health%20issues.%20When%20given%20a%20chance%20to%20speak%2C%20she%20said%20that%20she%20has%20prayed%20daily%20for%20forgiveness.%20%26quot%3BThere's%20so%20much%20pain%20that%20I%20have%20in%20regards%20to%20the%20loss%20of%20my%20baby%2C%20Jailyn%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%20in%20court.%20%26quot%3BI'm%20extremely%20hurt%20about%20everything%20that%20happened.%20I%20am%20not%20trying%20to%20justify%20my%20actions%2C%20but%20nobody%20knew%20how%20much%20I%20was%20suffering%20and%20what%20I%20was%20going%20through%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BGod%20and%20my%20daughter%20have%20forgiven%20me%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20claimed.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710868080000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2F7hfm4on8_kristel-candelario_625x300_19_March_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fus-woman-who-left-baby-home-alone-while-on-vacation-gets-life-sentence-5271145%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%2032-year-old%20woman%20in%20the%20United%20S