The%20MNS%20(Maharashtra%20Navnirman%20Sena)%20chief%2C%20who%20is%20also%20the%20estranged%20cousin%20of%20Mr%20Thackeray%2C%20was%20in%20Delhi%20today%2C%20ahead%20of%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections.%20He%20said%20he%20had%20been%20%26quot%3Bcalled%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20at%20a%20gathering%20in%20Nanded%20district%2C%20Uddhav%20Thackeray%20said%20the%20BJP%20%26quot%3Bknows%20very%20well%20that%20they%20don't%20get%20votes%20in%20the%20name%20of%20PM%20Narendra%20Modi%20in%20Maharashtra...%20People%20vote%20here%20in%20the%20name%20of%20(Bal)%20Thackeray%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20realisation%20prompted%20the%20BJP%20to%20try%20to%20steal%20leaders%20from%20outside.%C2%A0%20First%2C%20they%20stole%20the%20photo%20of%20Bal%20Thackeray%2C%20but%20it%20doesn't%20matter%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20in%20what%20was%20seen%20as%20an%20arch%20reference%20to%20Eknath%20Shinde%2C%20who%20is%20partnering%20the%20BJP.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Thackeray's%20Shiv%20Sena%20was%20split%20over%20what%20rebel%20leader%20Eknath%20Shinde%20--%20who%20subsequently%20became%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20of%20Maharashtra%20--%20called%20the%20legacy%20of%20party%20founder%20Bal%20Thackeray.%20The%20leader%2C%20who%20accused%20Mr%20Thackeray%20of%20deviating%20from%20the%20Hindutva%20ideology%20of%20Bal%20Thackeray%2C%20who%20was%20also%20his%20father%2C%20had%20later%20credited%20the%20BJP%20with%20masterminding%20the%20split.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BToday%2C%20they%20are%20trying%20to%20steal%20another%20Thackeray....take%20it.%20My%20people%20and%20I%20are%20enough%2C%26quot%3B%20Uddhav%20Thackeray%20then%20added%2C%20brushing%20off%20his%20cousin%20and%20the%20ultra%20slim%20niche%20appeal%20he%20has.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20MNS%2C%20formed%20in%202006%20after%20the%20cousins%20parted%20ways%20and%20depending%20on%20the%20anti-outsiders%20plank%2C%20has%20made%20little%20headway%20politically.%20From%2013%20assembly%20seats%20in%202008%2C%20it%20is%20now%20down%20to%20a%20single%20seat%2C%20won%20in%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Thackeray%2C%20whose%20party%20is%20part%20of%20the%20opposition%20Maha%20Vikas%20Aghadi%20and%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%2C%20also%20claimed%20even%20Christians%20and%20Muslims%20are%20comfortable%20with%20his%20brand%20of%20Hindutva.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20image%20of%20Shiv%20Sena%20(undivided)%20was%20getting%20sullied%20when%20we%20were%20with%20the%20BJP.%20But%20since%20we%20severed%20ties%20with%20them%2C%20even%20members%20of%20Christian%20and%20Muslim%20communities%20are%20saying%20that%20they%20have%20no%20issues%20with%20our%20Hindutva%20ideology%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESenior%20MNS%20leader%20Bala%20Nandgaonkar%20said%20the%20talks%20were%20%26quot%3Bpositive%26quot%3B.%20The%20MNS%2C%20it%20is%20learnt%2C%20wants%20three%20seats%20-%20South%20Mumbai%2C%20Shirdi%20and%20Nashik.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710867720000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2Fjcijcans_raj-thackeray-amit-shah_625x300_19_March_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ftrying-to-steal-a-thackeray-uddhav-thackeray-as-cousin-raj-thackeray-meets-amit-shah-5271034%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20BJP%20has%20realised%20that%20only%20the%20Thackeray%20name%20gets%20votes%20in%20Maharashtra%20and%20so%20they%20are%20trying%20to%20%26quot%3Bsteal%20a%20Thackeray%2C%26quot%3B%20former%20Chief%20Minister%20Uddhav%20Thackeray%20said%20today%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ftrying-to-steal-a-thackeray-uddhav-thackeray-as-cousin-raj-thackeray-meets-amit-shah-5271034%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ftrying-to-steal-a-thackeray-uddhav-thackeray-as-cousin-raj-thackeray-meets-amit-shah-5271034%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.