ontent%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710863004000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2018-01%2F08%2Ffull%2F1515365613-7295.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fsc-asks-ramdev-balkrishna-to-appear-personally-in-misleading-ads-case-124031901029_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20summon%20followed%20Patanjali%20Ayurved%20and%20Acharya%20Balkrishna's%20failure%20to%20respond%20to%20a%20contempt%20notice%20of%20the%20top%20court%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fsc-asks-ramdev-balkrishna-to-appear-personally-in-misleading-ads-case-124031901029_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fsc-asks-ramdev-balkrishna-to-appear-personally-in-misleading-ads-case-124031901029_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fsc-asks-ramdev-balkrishna-to-appear-personally-in-misleading-ads-case-124031901029_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Space%20Startup%20Agnikul%20Ready%20For%20Its%20Sub-Orbital%20Rocket%20Launch%20On%20Friday%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAgnikul%20Cosmos%2C%20India's%20private%20space%20start-up%2C%20will%20test-fire%20on%20Friday%20its%20rocket%20named%20Agnibaan%20SOrTeD%20(Suborbital%20Tech%20Demonstrator)%2C%20which%20is%20powered%20by%20an%20engine%20that%20the%20Indian%20Space%20Research%20Organisation%20(ISRO)%20is%20still%20trying%20to%20master.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIncubated%20at%20the%20Indian%20Institute%20of%20Technology-Madras%2C%20this%20will%20be%20the%20first%20test%20flight%20for%20the%202017%20born%20space%20start-up%20by%20two%20young%20aerospace%20engineers%20with%20a%20dream%20to%20create%20%26quot%3Ba%20place%20where%20people%20learn%20to%20use%20fire%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20580%20kilogram%20rocket%2C%20will%20lift%20off%20from%20Sriharikota%20and%20in%20the%20first%20flight%20could%20go%20only%20as%20high%20as%2020%20kilometres%20above%20the%20Earth%2C%20before%20plunging%20down%20into%20the%20Bay%20of%20Bengal%20and%20may%20carry%207%20kg%20of%20payloads.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Agnibaan%20SOrTeD%20will%20be%20powered%20by%20a%20semi-cryogenic%20engine%20that%20uses%20commercially%20available%20aviation%20turbine%20fuel%20or%20essentially%20kerosene%20and%20medical%20grade%20liquid%20oxygen%2C%20says%20Moin%20SPM%2C%20co-founder%20Agnikul%20Cosmos%20Pvt%20Ltd.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EISRO%20has%20never%20flown%20a%20semi-cryogenic%20engine%20and%20'the%20first%20hot%20test'%20of%20semi-cryogenic%20engine%20on%20a%20stationary%20test%20bed%20was%20conducted%20on%20July%203%20last%20year.%20The%20company%20is%20attempting%20what%20no%20other%20Indian%20private%20firm%20has%20done%20before.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAgnikul%20is%20demonstrating%20the%20first%20semi-cryogenic%20and%203D%20printed%20engine%20by%20the%20Indian%20private%20sector%2C%20says%20Dr%20Pawan%20Goenka%2C%20a%20highly%20regarded%20mechanical%20engineer%20and%20Chairperson%2C%20Indian%20National%20Space%20Promotion%20and%20Authorisation%20Centre%20(IN-SPACe)%2C%20part%20of%20the%20Department%20of%20Space%2C%20the%20single%20window%20regulator%20and%20promoter%20for%20all%20space%20activities%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Goenka%20says%20%26quot%3Bthis%20bold%20innovation%20could%20be%20a%20significant%20differentiator%20when%20commercial%20launches%20start%20by%20India's%20start%20ups%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20launch%20is%20significant%20since%20it%20is%20India's%20first%20launch%20from%20a%20private%20launch%20pad%20and%20the%20rocket%20has%20world's%20first%20single%20piece%203D%20printed%20engine%20designed%20and%20built%20indigenously%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Srinath%20Ravichandran%2C%20another%20co-founder%20of%20the%20space%20start-up.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAgnibaan%20SOrTeD%20(Suborbital%20Tech%20Demonstrator)%20is%20a%20single-stage%20launch%20vehicle%20driven%20by%20Agnikul's%20patented%20Agnilet%20engine%20-%20an%20entirely%203D-printed%2C%20single-piece%2C%206%20kN%20semi-cryogenic%20engine.%20Agnibaan%20SOrTeD%20will%20lift%20off%20vertically%20and%20follow%20a%20predetermined%20trajectory.%20The%20trajectory%2C%20manoeuvres%20and%20various%20flight%20events%20that%20will%20occur%20during%20the%20mission%20have%20been%20configured%20to%20validate%20tech%20integral%20to%20the%20success%20of%20our%20upcoming%20orbital%20flights.%20We%20are%20excited%20to%20be%20attempting%20this%20flight%20from%20our%20own%20launch%20pad%20named%20Dhanush%20at%20Sriharikota%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20company%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmong%20the%20many%20first%20for%20India%2C%20the%20Agnibaan%20rocket%20will%20be%20firing%20up%20on%20a%20special%203D%20printed%20engine%20which%20is%20single%20piece%20equipment%20and%20the%20quality%20testing%20time%20for%20such%20engines%20is%20highly%20reduced%20by%20using%203D%20printing%20technology%2C%20says%20Mr%20Moin.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20engine%20will%20also%20be%20powered%20by%20commercially%20available%20aviation%20turbine%20fuel%20and%20liquid%20oxygen%2C%20this%20makes%20for%20a%20cheap%20and%20easily%20available%20non%20corrosive%20fuel%20which%20is%20easily%20sourceable%2C%20says%20Mr%20Moin%2C%20adding%20this%20also%20makes%20launching%20of%20rockets%20from%20multiple%20locations%20with%20minimum%20facilities%20far%20easier.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20another%20first%2C%20Agnikul%20has%20been%20permitted%20to%20make%20a%20special%20launch%20pad%20near%20the%20sea%20on%20the%20island%20of%20Sriharikota%20with%20its%20own%20dedicated%20control%20room.%20This%20is%20part%20of%20ISRO%20opening%20up%20its%20facilities%20as%20part%20of%20ease%20of%20doing%20business%20for%20Indian%20space%20companies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20will%20be%20the%20first%20controlled%20flight%20of%20a%20rocket%20by%20a%20private%20company%20and%20all%20precautions%20are%20being%20taken%20to%20make%20sure%20nothing%20goes%20amiss%2C%20if%20things%20do%20go%20awry%20then%20the%20ISRO%20provided%20self-destruct%20mechanism%20can%20be%20activated%20by%20the%20Range%20Safety%20Officer%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Mr%20Moin.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAgnikul%20follows%20up%20on%20the%20first%20launch%20made%20by%20an%20Indian%20space%20company%20which%20was%20Skyroot%20Aerospace%20Private%20Limited%20which%20in%202022%20flew%20a%20solid%20fuelled%20sounding%20rocket%20from%20Sriharikota.%20Now%2C%20Agnikul%20with%20its%20Agnibaan%20rockets%2C%20when%20it%20becomes%20operational%2C%20hopes%20to%20undertake%20launch%20on%20demand%20and%20they%20hope%20to%20hoist%2030%20to%20300%20kilogram%20satellites%20into%20space.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20hope%20to%20build%20dedicated%2C%20fully%20customizable%20%26amp%3B%20transportable%20launch%20vehicles%20for%20small%20satellites%20to%20Low%20Earth%20Orbits%20(LEO).%20The%20launch%20vehicle-%20Agnibaan%20is%20powered%20by%20a%20single-piece%203D-printed%20engine%20that%20can%20be%20made%20in%2072%20hours%20without%20any%20human%20intervention.%20It%20is%20compatible%20with%20the%20mobile%20launch%20pad%20called%20%26quot%3BDhanush%26quot%3B%20which%20makes%20the%20launch%20location%20agnostic%20and%2C%20most%20importantly%2C%20it%20could%20be%20configured%20to%20fly%20with%204%2F5%2F6%2F7%20%5Bengines%5D%20which%20makes%20the%20launch%20cost%20the%20same%20across%20the%20spectrum%20of%20mass%20-%2030%20kg%20-%20300%20kg%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20the%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAgnikul%20has%20already%20attracted%20an%20investment%20of%20%2440%20million%20and%20has%20a%20team%20of%20250%20members.%20%26quot%3BThe%20average%20age%20of%20employees%20at%20Agnikul%20is%2023%20years%20and%20all%20are%20fired%20up%20to%20innovate%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Mr%20Moin%2C%20underscoring%20that%20India%20can%20become%20hub%20for%20small%20satellite%20launches%20as%20more%20and%20more%20global%20companies%20are%20opting%20for%20constellations%20of%20satellites%20placed%20in%20low%20earth%20orbits.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710862260000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2F9cv21scc_agnibaan-1200_625x300_19_March_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fspace-start-up-agnikul-ready-for-its-sub-orbital-rocket-agnibaan-launch-on-friday-5270592%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Agnikul%20Cosmos%2C%20India's%20private%20space%20start-up%2C%20will%20test-fire%20on%20Friday%20its%20rocket%20named%20Agnibaan%20SOrTeD%20(Suborbital%20Tech%20Demonstrator)%2C%20which%20is%20powered%20by%20an%20engine%20that%20the%20Indian%20Space%20Research%20Organisation%20(ISRO)%20is%20still%20trying%20to%20master.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fspace-start-up-agnikul-ready-for-its-sub-orbital-rocket-agnibaan-launch-on-friday-5270592%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fspace-start-up-agnikul-ready-for-its-sub-orbital-rocket-agnibaan-launch-on-friday-5270592%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fspace-start-up-agnikul-ready-for-its-sub-orbital-rocket-agnibaan-launch-on-friday-5270592%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Coimbatore%3A%20Inquiry%20Ordered%20Over%20Presence%20of%20Schoolchildren%20at%20PM%20Modi's%20Roadshow%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F19190947%2FUntitled-design-48-1.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ECoimbatore%20district%20education%20officer%20has%20ordered%20an%20inquiry%20over%20the%20participation%20of%20schoolchildren%20in%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20leader%20and%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20roadshow%20in%20Coimbatore%20on%20Monday%2C%20March%2018.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EModi%20undertook%20a%20four-kilometre-long%20roadshow%20between%20Ganga%20Hospital%20on%20Mettupalayam%20Road%20and%20the%20Head%20Post%20Office%20in%20RS%20Puram.%20Children%20under%2014%20from%20government-aided%20Sri%20Sai%20Baba%20Vidyalayam%20Aided%20Middle%20School%20were%20seen%20donning%20saffron-coloured%20cloth%20strips%20bearing%20party%20symbols%2C%20at%20various%20locations%20throughout%20the%20roadshow%2C%20performing%20on%20stages%20arranged%20by%20workers%20of%20the%20BJP.%20The%20participation%20of%20children%20in%20political%20rallies%20is%20against%20the%20directives%20of%20the%20Election%20Commission%20of%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAuthorities%20ordered%20school%20management%20to%20initiate%20strict%20action%20against%20the%20headmaster%20and%20staff%2C%20and%20also%20to%20submit%20a%20detailed%20report%20of%20the%20incident.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20taken%20cognisance%20of%20the%20issue%20and%20the%20ARO%20has%20sought%20reports%20from%20the%20respective%20departments.%20Suitable%20action%20will%20be%20taken%20based%20on%20the%20findings%20of%20the%20inquiry%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Coimbatore%20district%20collector%20in%20an%20X%20(Twitter)%20post.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeparate%20inquiries%20have%20also%20been%20initiated%20by%20the%20joint%20commissioner%20of%20the%20labour%20department%20and%20the%20chief%20education%20officer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20chief%20education%20officer%20M.%20Balamurali%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Felections%2Flok-sabha%2Fschoolchildren-at-pm-modis-coimbatore-road-show-inquiry-begins-into-poll-code-violations%2Farticle67967315.ece%5C%22%3Etold%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Hindu%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20initiated%20an%20investigation.%20Prior%20to%20the%20event%2C%20all%20schools%20were%20explicitly%20instructed%20to%20abstain%20from%20such%20practices.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAssistant%20Returning%20Officer%20(ARO)%20P.%20Suresh%2C%20spoke%20to%20the%20newspaper%2C%20confirming%20that%20these%20practices%20violate%20the%20Model%20Code%20of%20Conduct%20(MCC).%20%E2%80%9COnce%20the%20inquiry%20is%20concluded%2C%20reports%20will%20be%20forwarded%20to%20the%20Election%20Commission%20for%20further%20action%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710862188000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F19190947%2FUntitled-design-48-1.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fcoimbatore-inquiry-ordered-over-presence-of-schoolchildren-at-pm-modis-roadshow%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Children%20under%2014%20from%20a%20government-aided%20school%20were%20seen%20donning%20saffron-coloured%20cloth%20strips%20bearing%20BJP%20symbols%2C%20at%20various%20locations%20throughout%20the%20roadshow%20on%20March%2018%2C%20performing%20on%20stages%20arranged%20by%20workers%20of%20the%20BJP.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A4%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fcoimbatore-inquiry-ordered-over-presence-of-schoolchildren-at-pm-modis-roadshow%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Election%20Body%20Removes%20West%20Bengal%20Top%20Cop%20A%20Day%20After%20Appointment%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Election%20Commission%20on%20Tuesday%20removed%20Vivek%20Sahay%20as%20West%20Bengal%20DGP%2C%20less%20than%2024%20hours%20after%20naming%20him%20for%20the%20post%2C%20and%20directed%20the%20state%20government%20to%20appoint%20Sanjoy%20Mukherjee%2C%20a%20year%20junior%20to%20Sahay%20in%20the%20IPS%20cadre%2C%20in%20his%20place.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20move%2C%20unprecedented%20in%20recent%20memory%2C%20rendered%20Mr%20Sahay%20the%20shortest-serving%20DGP%20of%20West%20Bengal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESahay%2C%20an%20IPS%20officer%20of%20the%201988%20batch%2C%20was%20initially%20offered%20the%20appointment%20since%20he%20was%20the%20senior-most%20officer%20in%20the%20force.%20But%20owing%20to%20his%20scheduled%20superannuation%20on%20May%2031%2C%20well%20ahead%20of%20the%20formal%20conclusion%20of%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20on%20June%204%2C%20the%20poll%20panel%20considered%20naming%20Mukherjee%2C%20a%201989%20batch%20officer%2C%20as%20the%20DGP%2C%20a%20senior%20official%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMukherjee%2C%20the%20Director%20General%20of%20the%20state%20Fire%20%26amp%3B%20Emergency%20Services%20was%20the%20second%20on%20the%20list%20of%20the%20three%20officers%20recommended%20by%20the%20Bengal%20government%20for%20the%20post%20of%20DGP%20to%20the%20ECI%20after%20the%20poll%20panel%20directed%20the%20removal%20of%20Rajeev%20Kumar%20from%20that%20position%20in%20the%20run-up%20to%20the%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Monday%2C%20following%20an%20instruction%20of%20the%20ECI%20to%20post%20Rajeev%20Kumar%20to%20a%20%26quot%3Bnon-election%20related%20assignment%26quot%3B%2C%20and%2C%20as%20an%20interim%20arrangement%2C%20post%20an%20officer%20immediately%20junior%20to%20him%20as%20DGP%2C%20the%20Bengal%20government%20had%20named%20Sahay%20as%20replacement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECuriously%2C%20while%20Sahay's%20appointment%20notification%20was%20made%20by%20the%20state%20home%20department%20in%20which%20it%20referred%20to%20the%20ECI%20order%2C%20the%20corresponding%20notification%20for%20Mukherjee%20a%20day%20later%20was%20made%20directly%20by%20the%20Commission.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExplaining%20the%20sudden%20change%20of%20mind%20about%20the%20appointment%20of%20the%20state's%20top%20cop%2C%20a%20senior%20EC%20official%20told%20PTI%20that%20Sahay's%20was%20only%20an%20%26quot%3Binterim%20appointment%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20did%20not%20justify%2C%20though%2C%20why%20an%20appointment%20was%20notified%20by%20the%20state%20government%20would%20be%20toppled%20in%20less%20than%2024%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20official%20of%20the%20poll%20panel%2C%20however%2C%20said%20that%20Sahay%20was%20named%20the%20DGP%20based%20solely%20on%20his%20seniority%20and%20experience.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%20since%20he%20is%20supposed%20to%20retire%20in%20May%20even%20before%20the%20final%20round%20of%20polls%20on%20June%201%2C%20the%20ECI%20decided%20to%20make%20this%20change.%20If%20Sahay%20remained%20in%20the%20post%20of%20DGP%2C%20he%20would%20have%20to%20be%20changed%20again%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20the%20election%20process.%20That's%20why%20Mukherjee%20was%20given%20the%20charge%20instead%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20PTI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20former%20IPS%20officer%20in%20West%20Bengal%20cadre%20who%20served%20the%20state%20in%20senior%20positions%2C%20however%2C%20told%20PTI%20that%20the%20Commission%20retains%20the%20power%20to%20extend%20the%20tenure%20of%20an%20official%20if%20he%2Fshe%20was%20marked%20for%20any%20special%20assignment%2C%20such%20as%20the%20conduct%20of%20elections%2C%20by%20the%20poll%20body%20itself.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20am%20not%20convinced%20that%20the%20retirement%20clause%20is%20the%20only%20grounds%20for%20removing%20Sahay%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20former%20officer%2C%20requesting%20anonymity%2C%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSahay%20could%20have%20been%20easily%20retained%20as%20the%20DGP%20of%20the%20state%20till%20the%20elections%20got%20over.%20I%20believe%20we%20never%20had%20a%20DGP%20for%20such%20a%20small%20duration%20ever%20before%20in%20this%20country%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20March%202021%2C%20the%20ECI%20had%20suspended%20Sahay%2C%20then%20serving%20as%20director%20of%20security%2C%20following%20an%20incident%20in%20which%20Chief%20Minister%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20suffered%20a%20leg%20injury%20in%20Nandigram%20while%20campaigning%20for%20the%20assembly%20election%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20decision%20to%20suspend%20Sahay%20was%20based%20on%20reports%20submitted%20by%20the%20then%20chief%20secretary%20of%20West%20Bengal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBanerjee%20received%20injuries%20on%20her%20left%20foot%20in%20Nandigram%20on%20March%2011%2C%202021%2C%20while%20greeting%20her%20supporters%20standing%20on%20the%20footboard%20of%20her%20vehicle%20when%20her%20foot%20got%20caught%20between%20the%20front%20door%20and%20the%20seat%20of%20the%20car%20because%20of%20pressure%20from%20the%20crowd.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIncidentally%2C%20the%20poll%20panel%20had%20also%20removed%20Rajeev%20Kumar%20from%20active%20election%20management-related%20duties%20twice%20before%20--%20during%20the%202016%20assembly%20polls%20and%20the%202019%20general%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKumar%20was%20on%20Monday%20shifted%20to%20the%20Information%20and%20Technology%20department%2C%20an%20assignment%20not%20related%20to%20the%20elections.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710861720000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.ndtvimg.com%2Fi%2F2017-12%2Felection-commission-of-india_650x400_61513230434.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Felection-body-removes-bengal-top-cop-vivek-sahay-a-day-after-appointment-5270543%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Election%20Commission%20on%20Tuesday%20removed%20Vivek%20Sahay%20as%20West%20Bengal%20DGP%2C%20less%20than%2024%20hours%20after%20naming%20him%20for%20the%20post%2C%20and%20directed%20the%20state%20government%20to%20appoint%20Sanjoy%20Mukherjee%2C%20a%20year%20junior%20to%20Sahay.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Felection-body-removes-bengal-top-cop-vivek-sahay-a-day-after-appointment-5270543%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Felection