hat.%20I%20have%20only%20announced%2013%20seats%20%5Bfor%20Assam%5D%2C%20one%20is%20yet%20to%20be%20decided.%20After%20that%2C%20if%20they%20call%20me%2C%20I%20will%20definitely%20go.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESD%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cspan%3E%20Why%20do%20you%20think%20the%20Assam%20government%20is%20naming%20you%20in%20this%20case%20of%20property%20damage%20during%20the%20Bharat%20Jodo%20Nyay%20Yatra%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBB%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cspan%3E%20They%20%5Bthe%20Assam%20police%5D%20have%20registered%20cases%20against%20me%20under%20eight%20sections%2C%20of%20which%20two%20are%20non-bailable%2C%20in%20the%20Jorhat%20police%20station.%20I%20have%20already%20gone%20to%20the%20police%20station%20twice%2C%20where%20they%20have%20interrogated%20me%20for%20over%20six%20to%20seven%20hours.%20During%20the%20Yatra%20I%20was%20attacked%20as%20well.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%5BThe%20yatra%20used%5D%20The%20same%20venue%20where%20Modi%20addressed%20big%20public%20rallies%20%5Band%5D%20the%20same%20route%20that%20was%20used%20by%20J.P.%20Nadda%20to%20%5Btravel%20to%5D%20Batadrava%2C%20but%20Rahul%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Eji%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20was%20stopped.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESo%20as%20a%20symbol%20of%20protest%20we%20broke%20three%20barricades.%20There%20is%20nothing%20to%20hide%20because%20this%20took%20place%20in%20front%20of%20TV%20cameras.%20As%20%5BCongress%5D%20president%2C%20it%20was%20my%20duty%2C%20since%20my%20leader%20was%20waiting%20to%20go%20to%20Guwahati%20city.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Guwahati%20press%20club%20formally%20invited%20Rahul%20ji%20so%20we%20were%20just%20trying%20to%20go%20there%20to%20meet%20the%20media.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%20%7C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fbharat-jodo-nyay-yatra-at-right-time-to-keep-idea-of-india-alive-congress-mp-gaurav-gogoi%5C%22%3EBharat%20Jodo%20Nyay%20Yatra%20at%20Right%20Time%2C%20to%20Keep%20Idea%20of%20India%20Alive%3A%20Congress%20MP%20Gaurav%20Gogoi%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESD%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cspan%3E%20During%20the%20yatra%2C%20you%20were%20injured%20and%20you%20have%20said%20that%20the%20people%20who%20attacked%20you%20%E2%80%A6%20are%20walking%20free%2C%20while%20you%20are%20being%20summoned.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAre%20you%20saying%20that%20there%20has%20been%20inaction%20by%20the%20state%20government%20and%20targeted%20action%20against%20you%20and%20other%20Congress%20leaders%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBB%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cspan%3E%20From%20the%20very%20beginning%2C%20the%20CM%20first%20tried%20to%20purchase%20me.%20So%20many%20people%20close%20to%20the%20CM%20contacted%20me%20and%20asked%20me%2C%20%E2%80%98What%20%5Bdo%5D%20you%20want%2C%20your%20energy%20will%20be%20wasted%2C%20you%20should%20join%20us%20%5Bthe%20BJP%5D.%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFor%20six%20months%20they%20tried%20and%20when%20they%20found%20that%20I%20am%20committed%20to%20my%20ideology%20and%20my%20party%20leader%2C%20then%20they%20served%20three%20notices%20to%20demolish%20my%20house%20in%20Guwahati.%20But%20due%20to%20civil%20society%20support%2C%20my%20house%20is%20still%20there.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThey%20transferred%20my%20wife%2C%20who%20is%20associate%20professor%20in%20Guwahati%20Medical%20College%2C%20then%20they%20transferred%20my%20brother%20and%20my%20sister-in-law%2C%20and%20lastly%20they%20physically%20attacked%20me%20during%20the%20Bharat%20Jodo%20Nyay%20Yatra.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThey%20have%20also%20reduced%20my%20security.%20So%20first%20they%20tried%20to%20purchase%20me%2C%20but%20now%20they%20are%20trying%20to%20threaten%20me.%20But%20I%20assure%20the%20people%20of%20Assam%20and%20my%20leadership%20that%20I%20will%20not%20compromise.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESD%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cspan%3E%20In%20recent%20weeks%2C%20we%20have%20seen%20a%20series%20of%20desertions%20by%20Congress%20leaders%20in%20Assam%20before%20elections%2C%20including%20former%20working%20presidents%20Kamalakhya%20Dey%20Purkayastha%2C%20who%20declared%20his%20support%20for%20the%20BJP%2C%20and%20Rana%20Goswami%3B%20MLA%20Basanta%20Das%3B%20and%20former%20general%20secretary%20Suruj%20Dehingia%2C%20who%20have%20joined%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIs%20the%20Assam%20Congress%20failing%20to%20keep%20its%20flock%20together%20before%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBB%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cspan%3E%20I%20cannot%20take%20action%20against%20MLAs%2C%20as%20they%20are%20under%20the%20AICC%20%5BAll%20India%20Congress%20Committee%5D%E2%80%99s%20jurisdiction.%20From%20the%20time%20of%20the%20presidential%20elections%20%5Bwhen%20Congress%20MLAs%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feconomictimes.indiatimes.com%2Fnews%2Fpolitics-and-nation%2Fassam-25-mlas-belonging-to-opposition-camp-cross-voted-in-in-favour-of-nda-candidate%2Farticleshow%2F93057411.cms%3Ffrom%3Dmdr%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ecross-voted%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20against%20the%20opposition%20candidate%20Yashwant%20Sinha%20in%202022%5D%2C%20we%20know%20Himanta%20Biswa%E2%80%99s%20agents%20are%20within%20us.%20Now%20they%20are%20leaving%20us.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20have%20said%20before%20also%20that%20we%20want%20a%20Himanta%20Biswa-mukt%20Congress.%20He%20was%20in%20the%20Congress%20for%20so%20many%20years%20%5Band%20so%5D%20he%20has%20maintained%20friendships.%20There%20are%20many%20second-line%20leaders%20who%20will%20come%20forward.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%2