C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThey%20use%20it%20for%20everything%20from%20travelling%20in%20the%20city%20to%20buying%20groceries.%20That%20means%20that%20these%20families%20need%20their%20two-wheelers%20to%20have%20ample%20space%2C%20efficiency%20and%20be%20cost-effective%2C%E2%80%9D%20Arvind%20Mani%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECracking%20the%20code%2C%20Arvind%2C%20along%20with%20his%20co-founder%2C%20Vipin%20George%2C%20made%20their%20electric%20two-wheeler%20with%2055%20litre%20of%20storage%20space%2C%20packing%20it%20with%20numerous%20qualities.%20Calling%20it%20the%20%E2%80%98SUV%20of%20Scooters%E2%80%99%2C%20Indie%20is%20an%20electric%20two-wheeler%20built%20under%20River.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20recently%20raised%20an%20investment%20of%20%2440%20million%20(Rs%20335%20crore)%20globally%20in%20an%20oversubscribed%20Series%20B%20round%20(second%20round%20of%20funding).%20Interestingly%2C%20Yamaha%20Motor%20Company%20and%20UAE%20automotive%20giant%2C%20Al-Futtaim%2C%20are%20among%20its%20top%20investors.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFor%20the%20youth%20of%20the%20country%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECalling%20their%20partnership%20a%20perfect%20match%2C%20Arvind%20explains%20how%20their%20work%20at%20the%20startup%20is%20divided.%20%E2%80%9CVipin%20is%20a%20hardcore%20automobile%20guy%20and%20I%20know%20how%20to%20sell%20things.%20The%20combination%20is%20perfect%20and%20we%20both%20handle%20our%20respective%20areas%20of%20expertise%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoth%20the%20co-founders%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F332097%2Fkerala-sustainable-home-disaster-resistant-ecofriendly-lgsf-technology%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20are%20from%20Kerala%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20met%20through%20a%20common%20company%20where%20the%20duo%20worked.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20both%20grew%20up%20in%20small%20towns%20and%20we%20believe%20that%20India%20has%20massive%20potential.%20The%20youth%20in%20our%20small%20towns%20have%20great%20potential%2C%20especially%20in%20the%20manufacturing%20sector%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FEV-4-1710756836.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Besides%20the%2055%20L%20cargo%2C%20the%20vehicle%20also%20has%20a%2012-litre%20lockable%20glove%20box%20with%20a%20USB%20charger.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FEV-4-1710756836.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FEV-4-1710756836-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FEV-4-1710756836-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FEV-4-1710756836-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FEV-4-1710756836-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-345054%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EBesides%20the%2055%20L%20cargo%2C%20the%20vehicle%20also%20has%20a%2012-litre%20lockable%20glove%20box%20with%20a%20USB%20charger.%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWanting%20to%20utilise%20this%20potential%2C%20the%20duo%20decided%20to%20start%20their%20own%20company.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20were%20sure%20that%20whatever%20we%20produce%20will%20be%20manufactured%20by%20us%20in%20order%20to%20utilise%20the%20massive%20talent%20in%20the%20country%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBeing%20an%20automotive%20guy%2C%20we%20were%20very%20sure%20that%20this%20is%20the%20industry%20we%20wanted%20to%20enter.%20But%20this%20centuries-old%20industry%20is%20a%20tough%20one%20to%20enter.