%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBesides%20utility%2C%20what%20they%20wanted%20to%20focus%20on%20as%20a%20company%20was%20the%20design.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FEV-5-1710756910.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Vipin%20George%20and%20Arvind%20Mani%2C%20founders%20of%20River.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FEV-5-1710756910.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FEV-5-1710756910-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FEV-5-1710756910-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FEV-5-1710756910-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FEV-5-1710756910-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-345055%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EVipin%20George%20and%20Arvind%20Mani%2C%20founders%20of%20River.%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20India%2C%20we%20noticed%20that%20if%20something%20is%20high%20in%20utility%2C%20then%20its%20design%20is%20neglected.%20However%2C%20since%20we%20want%20to%20appeal%20to%20the%20youth%2C%20we%20want%20to%20give%20them%20the%20best%20design%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20youth%20knows%20what%20they%20want%20from%20the%20vehicle%20but%20also%20they%20want%20it%20to%20have%20some%20personality.%20So%20this%20became%20our%20driving%20force%2C%20we%20combine%20utility%20with%20design%20to%20create%20a%20product%20that%20is%20eco-friendly%20and%20suits%20our%20users.%20Just%20as%20a%20farmer%20drives%20his%20truck%20or%20tractor%20with%20pride%2C%20we%20want%20a%20small%20entrepreneur%2C%20say%20a%20carpenter%2C%20to%20have%20pride%20in%20driving%20his%20business%20vehicle%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20scooter%20has%20the%20largest%20storage%20capacity%20of%2055%20litre%20which%20is%20three%20times%20more%20than%20the%20average%20scooter%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20also%20have%20the%20largest%20floor%20board%20since%20people%20utilise%20every%20inch%20of%20the%20vehicle%20in%20India.%20You%20will%20often%20see%20grocery%20bags%2C%20school%20bags%2C%20and%20even%20kids%20standing%20on%20them.%20So%20in%20our%20product%2C%20we%20have%20included%20%E2%80%98Lock%20and%20Load%20Pannier%20Mounts%E2%80%99%2C%20which%20are%20sturdy%20alloy%20mounts%20on%20both%20sides%20of%20the%20scooter.%20Attach%20pannier%20boxes%2C%20load%20up%20and%20make%20the%20most%20of%20the%20day%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20love%20the%20hustle%20culture%20of%20our%20youth%20and%20we%20have%20made%20a%20vehicle%20designed%20especially%20for%20that%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20vehicle%20also%20has%20a%2012-litre%20lockable%20glove%20box%20with%20a%20USB%20charger.%20%E2%80%9CStore%20and%20lock%20up%20your%20valuables%20for%20safety%2C%20and%20easily%20access%20them%20while%20being%20seated%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20about%20the%20range%20anxiety%20that%20most%20people%20deal%20with%2C%20he%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20scooters%20are%20usually%20used%20by%20Indians%20to%20drive%20within%20the%20cities%20and%20inter-city%20usage%20is%20usually%20via%20a%20motorcycle.%20Designed%20specifically%20for%20inter-city%20travel%2C%20we%20have%20offered%20a%20range%20of%20103%20km%20when%20fully-charged.%20So%20this%20way%2C%20a%20customer%20will%20be%20charging%20the%20vehicle%20once%20every%20three%20to%20four%20days.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagr