e%20Sunetra.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20followed%20Ajit%20all%20the%20time...%20in%20all%20situations.%20I%20supported%20decisions%20and%20never%20questioned%20him.%20Many%20people%20know%20me%20here%20(Baramati)...%20I%20grew%20up%20here.%20When%20Ajit%20and%20I%20had%20a%20discussion%2C%20I%20told%20him%2C%20'you%20keep%20contesting%20Baramati%20as%20MLA%20and%20leave%20Lok%20Sabha%20under%20Pawar%20saheb's%20leadership...%20as%20we%20are%20grateful%20to%20him%20for%20various%20things%20he%20did%20for%20us.%20I%20didn't%20feel%20good%20about%20leaving%20him%20alone%20at%2083.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPawar%20senior%20also%20said%20the%2083-year-old%20Sharad%20Pawar%20had%20done%20a%20lot%20for%20the%20family.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSome%20of%20our%20friends%20told%20me%20the%20future%20lies%20with%20Ajit%20instead%20of%20Sharad...%20but%20this%20thought%20was%20very%20painful.%20(I%20don't)%20want%20to%20leave%20a%20person%20in%20their%20old%20age...%20a%20person%20who%20can%20benefit%20us.%20In%20my%20personal%20view%2C%20if%20someone%20thinks%20in%20such%20a%20way%2C%20he%20is%20an%20incompetent%20person%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20declared.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShrinivas%20Pawar%20wasn't%20done%20yet.%20He%20also%20accused%20Ajit%20of%20standing%20on%20the%20shoulder%20of%20their%20uncle%20for%20political%20gain%2C%20and%20then%20casting%20him%20aside%2C%20and%20then%20appeared%20to%20signal%20a%20break%20with%20his%20brother.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20like%20removing%20the%20owner%20of%20a%20house%20after%20getting%20ownership%20of%20the%20land.%20We%20all%20know%20whoever%20got%20positions%20in%20politics...%20it%20was%20because%20of%20Sharad%20Pawar.%20Like%20medicines%20(which%20have%20an%20expiry%20date)%20some%20relationships%20also%20expire.%20I%20am%2060...%20I%20can't%20live%20under%20pressure%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShrinivas%20Pawar's%20broadside%20at%20his%20brother%20was%20a%20stinging%20one%2C%20but%20it%20was%20unlikely%20that%20it%20was%20an%20unexpected%20one%3B%20last%20month%20the%20Deputy%20Chief%20Minister%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BMy%20entire%20family%20will%20now%20be%20against%20me.%20They%20will%20campaign%20against%20me...%20but%20my%20workers%20are%20my%20family%20now.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20particular%20Pawar%20versus%20Pawar%20squabble%20comes%20as%20Ajit%20Pawar's%20faction%20faced%20a%20setback%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20in%20a%20battle%20for%20the%20undivided%20NCP's%20clock%20symbol.%20It%2C%20and%20the%20NCP%20name%2C%20was%20given%20to%20Ajit%20Pawar%20by%20the%20Election%20Commission%2C%20but%20the%20Sharad%20Pawar%20camp%20has%20challenged%20that%20award.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmockery-of-voters-supreme-court-in-pawar-versus-pawar-hearing-5268949%23pfrom%3Dhome-ndtv_topscroll%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BMockery%20Of%20Voters%26quot%3B%3A%20Supreme%20Court%20In%20Pawar%20versus%20Pawar%20Hearing%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20has%2C%20for%20now%2C%20said%20the%20Ajit%20Pawar%20camp%20gets%20the%20symbol%2C%20but%20only%20with%20suitable%20disclaimers%20in%20all%20instances%20of%20use.%20The%20court%20also%20questioned%20the%20poll%20panel's%20recognition%20of%20the%20Ajit%20Pawar%20camp%20as%20the%20%26quot%3Breal%26quot%3B%20NCP%2C%20just%20as%20it%20recognised%20Chief%20Minister%20Eknath%20Shinde's%20Sena%20as%20the%20%26quot%3Breal%20Shiv%20Sena%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20July%20last%20year%2C%20Pawar%20junior%20forced%20a%20break%20within%20the%20Nationalist%20Congress%20Party%20founded%20and%20led%20by%20Sharad%20Pawar%3B%20Ajit%20Pawar%20led%2040%2B%20MLAs%20into%20the%20waiting%20arms%20of%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%2C%20strengthening%20the%20BJP-Shinde%20Shiv%20Sena%20faction's%20control%20of%20the%20Maharashtra%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%