ttps%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia-indiatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fchina%2Fwill-help-guard-against-colour-revolution-hong-kong-passes-national-security-bill-tightening-chinas-grip%2Famp_articleshow%2F108620128.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fchina%2Fwill-help-guard-against-colour-revolution-hong-kong-passes-national-security-bill-tightening-chinas-grip%2Famp_articleshow%2F108620128.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Bigotry%20On%20Display%3A%20Muslims%20Shown%20As%20Criminals%20In%20Bodoland%20University%E2%80%99s%20Cultural%20Event%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F19150225%2FScreen-Shot-2024-03-19-at-3.01.48-PM.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20A%20cultural%20procession%20organised%20by%20the%20Department%20of%20History%20at%20the%20Bodoland%20University%20in%20Kokrajhar%2C%20Assam%20took%20a%20disturbing%20turn%20when%20it%20depicted%20Muslims%20as%20criminals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20incident%20took%20place%20on%20March%2016%20where%20a%20cultural%20event%20intended%20as%20a%20celebration%20of%20video%20legendary%20heroes%20during%20the%20university%E2%80%99s%2023rd%20varsity%20week%20and%20Thulunga%20Festival%20was%20being%20held.%20However%2C%20a%20viral%20video%20showed%20a%20stage%20act%20where%20two%20people%20were%20dressed%20in%20Muslim%20attire%2C%20with%20beards%20and%20skull%20caps%2C%20and%20also%20had%20their%20hands%20bound.%20They%20were%20being%20walked%20in%20the%20rally%20behind%20a%20man%20reportedly%20dressed%20up%20as%20a%20policeman.%20The%20two%20dressed%20up%20people%20are%20shown%20to%20be%20beaten%20up%20by%20police%20personnel%20in%20the%20video%20of%20the%20rally.%20The%20rally%2C%20with%20students%20holding%20up%20the%20banner%20for%20the%20event%2C%20can%20be%20seen%20following%20behind.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20has%20drawn%20condemnation%20from%20students%20and%20organisations%20in%20the%20state.%20In%20response%20to%20the%20incident%2C%20according%20to%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnenow.in%2Fnorth-east-news%2Fassam%2Fassam-bodoland-university-portrays-muslims-as-criminals-in-cultural-processionn.html%5C%22%3ENortheast%20Now%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20Muslim%20Student%20Union%20of%20Assam%E2%80%99s%20(MSUA)%20central%20president%20Jalal%20Uddin%20expressed%20shock%20at%20the%20depiction%20and%20promised%20action%20if%20the%20university%20fails%20to%20address%20the%20matter%20promptly.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20do%20not%20understand%20why%20a%20higher%20educational%20institute%20tried%20to%20portray%20Muslims%20as%20criminals.%20We%20condemn%20the%20attitude%20of%20Bodoland%20University%20for%20such%20humiliation.%20The%20entire%20community%20is%20not%20responsible%20for%20an%20act%20of%20a%20certain%20person.%20We%20will%20wait%20for%20two%20days.%20If%20the%20university%20authority%20does%20not%20clarify%20the%20issue%2C%20we%20will%20lodge%20an%20FIR%20against%20them.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20the%20report%2C%20other%20student%20organisations%20including%20North%20East%20Minority%20Students%20Union%20(NEMU)%2C%20Krishak%20Shramiak%20Unnayan%20Sangram%20Samiti%20(KSUSS)%2C%20Muslim%20Jatiya%20Parishad%20(MJP)%2C%20and%20Burman%20Mandai%20Students%20Union%20(BMSU)%20have%20also%20condemned%20the%20incident.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20incident%20raises%20concerns%20about%20Muslims%20in%20Assam.%20According%20to%20the%202011%20Indian%20census%2C%20Muslims%20make%20up%20about%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.census2011.co.in%2Fdata%2Freligion%2Fstate%2F18-assam.html%5C%22%3E35%25%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0of%20the%20population%20of%20Assam%2C%20the%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fguwahati%2Fassam-cabinet-approves-census-of-native-muslims%2Farticleshow%2F105849216.cms%5C%22%3E%C2%A0third%20highest%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0among%20Indian%20states.%20However%2C%20despite%20there%20being%20a%20significant%20presence%20in%20the%20state%20their%20representation%20in%20positions%20of%20power%20remains%20disproportionately%20low%20as%20according%20to%20a%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fwhither-assam-muslims-the-story-of-groups-exclusion-from-political-public-spheres%5C%22%3Ereport%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E.%20The%20report%20stated%20that%20Muslims%20are%20often%20subjected%20to%20stereotypes%20and%20names%20such%20as%20%E2%80%9CBangladeshi%E2%80%9D%2C%20%E2%80%9Cillegal%20immigrant%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9CJihadi%E2%80%9D%20and%20considered%20to%20be%20%E2%80%98outsiders%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%E2%80%99s%3C%2Fem%3E%20analysis%20from%20January%202024%20underlined%20that%20Assam%20has%20given%2016%20ministers%20to%20the%20Parliament%2C%20however%2C%20not%20one%20of%20them%20is%20a%20Muslim.%20Similarly%2C%20it%20notes%20that%20across%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%2034%20districts%2C%20there%20is%20not%20even%20one%20Muslim%20deputy%20commissioner%20(DC).%20There%20are%20also%20reportedly%20no%20Muslim%20superintendents%20of%20police%20(SP)%20in%20any%20of%20these%20districts%20either.%20The%20analysis%20also%20looks%20at%20the%20composition%20in%20the%20judicial%20system%20and%20notes%20that%20even%20though%20the%20Gauhati%20high%20court%20comprises%2023%20judges%2C%20there%20is%20no%20judge%20from%20the%20Muslim%20community%20in%20the%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20also%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fwhither-assam-muslims-the-story-of-groups-exclusion-from-political-public-spheres%5C%22%3Enoted%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0the%20composition%20of%20Muslim%20teachers%20in%20the%20state%20and%20noted%20that%2C%20amongst%20others%2C%20out%20of%20the%2093%20teachers%20at%20Bodoland%20University%2C%20the%20university%20did%20not%20have%20a%20single%20Muslim%20teacher%2C%20in%20permanent%20or%20non-permanent%20posts.%20However%2C%20interestingly%20the%20only%20place%20where%20Muslim%20presence%20is%20notably%20high%20is%20among%20undertrials%20in%20the%20state%20and%20the%20percentage%20stands%20at%20a%20staggering%2052.54%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAssam%20chief%20minister%20Himanta%20Biswa%20Sarma%20has%20also%20been%20in%20the%20past%20recorded%20for%20reportedly%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsabrangindia.in%2Fec-issues-show-cause-notice-to-assam-cm-himanta-biswa-sarma-for-communal-speech%2F%5C%22%3Egiving%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsabrangindia.in%2Ftrend-of-divisive-politics-continues-3-hate-speeches-by-assam-cm-in-poll-bound-states%2F%5C%22%3Ehate%20speeches%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0and%20also%20engaging%20in%20dog-whistling%20against%20minorities.%20In%202023%2C%20he%20once%20even%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fother-states%2Fassam-cm-blames-miyas-for-costlier-vegetable-opposition-slams-sarma%2Farticle67084075.ece%5C%22%3Eblamed%C2%A0%3C%2Fa%3Ethe%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3EMiya%3C%2Fem%3E%20Muslims%E2%80%99%20of%20Assam%20for%20the%20hike%20in%20vegetable%20prices.%20%3Cem%3EMiya%3C%2Fem%3E%20is%20reportedly%20a%20derogatory%20term%20to%20refer%20to%20Bengali%20speaking%20Muslims%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsabrangindia.in%2Fbodoland-universitys-cultural-event-reportedly-displays-muslims-as-criminals-escorted-by-police-student-groups-demand-apology%2F%5C%22%3Earticle%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0was%20originally%20published%20on%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsabrangindia.in%2F%5C%22%3ESabrangIndia%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710849619000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F19150225%2FScreen-Shot-2024-03-19-at-3.01.48-PM.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fbigotry-on-display-muslims-shown-as-criminals-in-bodoland-universitys-cultural-event%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22It%20has%20drawn%20