1024.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22318%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F20144212%2FIMG_2915-1-746x1024.jpg%20746w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F20144212%2FIMG_2915-1-219x300.jpg%20219w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F20144212%2FIMG_2915-1.jpg%20874w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-697965%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22437%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EIllustration%3A%20Pariplab%20Chakraborty.%20Photo%3A%20Intifada%20P.%20Basheer%20and%20Azam%20Abbas%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThose%20who%20were%20allegedly%20made%20to%20attend%20the%20event%20came%20from%20departments%20such%20as%20school%20education%2C%20higher%20education%2C%20agriculture%2C%20social%20welfare%20and%20the%20Srinagar%20municipal%20corporation.%20Locals%20who%20were%20barred%20from%20attending%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fwed-high-hopes-of-meeting-the-pm-say-kashmiris-who-werent-allowed-to-enter-the-stadium%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Esaid%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3Ethat%20they%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Ewanted%20to%20talk%20to%20the%20Modi%20about%20their%20problems.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBeing%20left%20out%20was%20almost%20like%20a%20metaphor%20for%20them.%20For%20many%2C%20it%20was%20a%20reminder%20of%20how%20the%20job%20market%20had%20forgotten%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%E2%80%99s%20youth.%20Akhter%2C%20an%20unemployed%20graduate%2C%20who%20requested%20that%20he%20only%20be%20mentioned%20by%20his%20first%20name%2C%20asks%2C%20%E2%80%9CShould%20we%20hope%20for%20jobs%20or%20should%20we%20not%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EFrom%20calculations%20to%20cafes%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWhile%20hunting%20for%20jobs%2C%20I%20ended%20up%20completing%20degrees%20just%20for%20measly%20recruitment%20drives%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20one%20Iqbal%20Ahmed.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CI%20completed%20my%20MSc%20in%20Biotechnology%20in%202016.%20Then%20I%20did%20a%20BEd%20degree%20for%20some%20posts%20that%20were%20announced.%20Thousands%20would%20apply%20for%20five%20to%20six%20teaching%20job%20posts.%20Then%20I%20also%20did%20a%20two-year%20diploma%20course%20in%20Operation%20Theatre%20training.%20Despite%20all%20this%2C%20I%20am%20jobless%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Ahmed.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAhmed%20says%20he%20took%20various%20loans%20from%20friends%20and%20family%2C%20to%20invest%20in%20a%20Kashmiri%20caf%C3%A9%20brand%2C%20which%20has%20over%2035%20outlets%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20and%20mainland%20India.%20Ahmed%20credits%20Kashmiri%20entrepreneur%20Javid%20Parsa%20for%20mentoring%20him%20when%20he%20needed%20it%20the%20most.%20His%20degrees%2C%20he%20stresses%2C%20proved%20useless.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CToday%2C%20I%20am%20not%20a%20job%20seeker%2C%20by%20Allah%E2%80%99s%20grace%2C%20I%E2%80%99m%20a%20job%20giver%E2%80%9D%20Ahmed%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EParsa%2C%20founder%20of%20a%20Kashmiri%20restaurant%20chain%2C%20has%20had%20his%20share%20of%20mentoring%20hundreds%20of%20educated%20yet%20unemployed%20youth.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20main%20motivation%20behind%20leaving%20my%20corporate%20job%20in%20Hyderabad%20and%20returning%20to%20Kashmir%20in%202014%20was%20essentially%20so%20I%20could%20help%20my%20people%20amidst%20this%20absolute%20dearth%20of%20job%20opportunities%2C%E2%80%9D%20Parsa%20says.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EParsa%20believes%20that%20there%20is%20a%20massive%20youth%20population%20in%20the%20Union%20Territory%20which%20is%20unemployed%20and%20now%20unmoved%20by%20the%20political%20promises%20made%20to%20them.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20I%20share%20job%20openings%20at%20my%20restaurant%2C%20exceptionally%20educated%20graduates%20and%20post-graduates%20contact%20me%20for%20wait%20staff%20jobs%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20tells%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20adds%20that%20the%20private%20sector%20is%20as%20good%20as%20non-existent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EDecaying%20degrees%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EEach%20morning%20Afshan%20Rashid%20travels%20a%20distance%20of%2060%20kms%20from%20Ganderbal%20to%20reach%20her%20ancestral%20land%20in%20Pulwama%E2%80%99s%20Lassipora.%20%E2%80%9CFarming%20is%20an%20intense%2C%20mindful%20and%20continuous%20activity%2C%20it%20requires%20utmost%20attention%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20explains.%20%E2%80%9CMy%20usual%20farm%20day%20consists%20of%20many%20activities%20such%20as%20feeding%20chickens%2C%20milking%20cows%2C%20watering%20shrubbery%20and%20trees%2C%20switching%20on%20drip%20irrigation%2C%20de-weeding%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERashid%2C%20a%20media%20professional%20by%20education%20chose%20the%20farming%20life%20out%20of%20affection%20for%20her%20mother.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20started%20this%20initiative%20on%20a%20small%20scale%2C%20and%20started%20receiving%20such%20great%20response%20on%20Instagram%20for%20these%20simple%20farm%20videos%20we%20would%20post.%20Many%20unemployed%20persons%20would%20tell%20us%20how%20their%20unemployment%20%E2%80%93%20despite%20the%20fact%20that%20they%20were%20educated%20%E2%80%93%20was%20making%20them%20consider%20farming%20to%20earn%20a%20living%2C%E2%80%9D%20Rashid%20says.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERashid%20too%20tries%20to%20mentor%20as%20many%20unemployed%20young%20men%20and%20women%20as%20possible%2C%20and%20tries%20to%20guide%20them%20towards%20government%20schemes%20and%20subsidies%20that%20help%20budding%20farmers.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMusaib%20Nazeer%2C%20an%20MBA%20graduate%2C%20is%20currently%20running%20a%20branch%20of%20Parsa%E2%80%99s%20restaurant%20in%20Srinagar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENazeer%20says%20he%20struggled%20to%20adjust%20to%20the%20reality%20that%20so%20few%20job%20options%20were%20available%20in%20the%20region.%20%E2%80%9CThere%20is%20a%20lot%20of%20unemployment%20here%20and%20this%20creates%20a%20whole%20new%20layer%20of%20challenges.%20Over-qualified%20individuals%20are%20forced%20to%20settle%20for%20jobs%20which%20do%20not%20match%20their%20calibre.%20This%20negates%20the%20whole%20idea%20of%20education%2C%E2%80%9D%20Nazeer%20says%2C%20adding%20that%20it%20is%20common%20to%20have%20over-qualified%20people%20apply%20in%20various%20capacities%20at%20the%20restaurant%20he%20manages.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERiyaz%20Bhat%2C%20a%20graduate%20in%20political%20science%20knows%20this%20all%20too%20well.%20At%2029%2C%20he%20currently%20works%20as%20a%20waiter.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20government%20should%20think%20about%20us%2C%20give%20us%20ways%20to%20put%20our%20knowledge%20to%20use%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDr.%20Uzma%20Saleem%20Malik%2C%20lecturer%20at%20a%20government%20college%20in%20Jammu%2C%20has%20seen%20the%20impact%20that%20lack%20of%20opportunities%20can%20have%20on%20the%20educated%20unemployed%20very%20closely.%20Due%20to%20the%20absence%20of%20a%20robust%20private%20sector%20or%20corporate%20culture%2C%20several%20educated%20persons%20in%20the%20region%20are%20also%20desperately%20trying%20to%20crack%20government%20job%20exams.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20brutal.%20Sometimes%20when%20I%20review%20ID%20cards%20while%20conducting%20exams%2C%20I%20see%20that%20those%20born%20in%20the%20late%2080s%20are%20still%20trying%20to%20crack%20SSB%20exams%20which%20offer%20meagre%20salaries%2C%E2%80%9D%20Malik%20says.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMalik%20also%20juxtaposes%20the%20situation%20to%20those%20in%20metro%20cities.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CA%20qualified%20PhD%20holder%20in%20Delhi%2C%20or%20any%20other%20metro%20city%2C%20is%20bound%20to%20have%20various%20avenues%20to%20gain%20employment.%20Here%2C%20posts%20are%20few%2C%20work%20expectation%20is%20massive%20and%20salaries%20are%20miniscule.%20There%20are%20only%20a%20handful%20universities%20here%2C%20they%20also%20may%20or%20may%20not%20advertise%20posts%20of%20all%20departments.%20That%20also%20restricts%20employment%20opportunities.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERequesting%20anonymity%2C%20a%20PhD%20scholar%20from%20Kashmir%20said%20that%20after%20completing%20her%20PhD%20in%20a%20political%20science%20topic%2C%20she%20had%20qualified%20for%20the%20University%20Grants%20Commission%E2%80%99s%20National%20Eligibility%20Test%20and%20State-Level%20Eligibility%20Test.%20She%20claimed%20that%20for%20an%20assistant%20professor%E2%80%99s%20job%20alone%2C%20s%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Echolars%20of%20this%20region%20face%20verification%20attempts%20by%20police%20and%20other%20investigation%20departments.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOther%20locals%20whom%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20spoke%20to%20said%20that%20private%20sector%20in%20the%20region%20has%20been%20reduced%20to%20handicrafts%2C%20hospitality%2C%20and%20entrepreneurship.%20Despite%20political%20claims%2C%20they%20argued%2C%20there%20was%20no%20investment%20by%20private%20players%20in%20the%20region%20in%20education%2C%20research%20and%20civil%20society%20organisations.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20December%202022%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Edata%20released%20by%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Home%20Affairs%20revealed%20that%20the%20total%20investment%20in%20the%20region%20in%202021-22%20was%20Rs%20376.76%20crore%2C%20down%20from%20Rs%20412.74%20crore%20in%202020-21%20and%20a%20massive%20drop%20of%2055%25%20from%20Rs%20840.55%20crore%20in%202017-18.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EDisappointing%20data%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EApart%20from%20rising%20dissatisfaction%20and%20decaying%20degrees%2C%20restricted%20job%20prospects%20are%20pushing%20Kashmiri%20students%20to%20reassess%20their%20educational%20trajectories.%20In%202023%2C%20the%20admission%20rate%20in%20educational%20institutions%20in%20the%20region%20was%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ffrontline.thehindu.com%2Fsociety%2Fjammu-and-kashmir-saw-the-highest-attempted-suicide-rate-in-india-in-2022%2Farticle67744235.ece%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eappallingly%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20low%20with%20colleges%20witnessing%20a%2040.6%20%25%20decrease%20in%20admissions.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EJavid%20Ahmed%20Tenga%2C%20president%20of%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EKashmir%20Chamber%20of%20Commerce%20and%20Industry%20(KCCI)%20told%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3Ethat%20to%20deal%20with%20the%20unemployment%20numbers%2C%20there%20must%20be%20such%20policies%20introduced%20by%20the%20government%20which%20cater%20to%20both%20the%20uneducated%20and%20educated.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20definitely%20need%20drives%20to%20skill%20the%20unemployed%2C%20as%20for%20the%20educated%20unemployed%2C%20private%20sector%20needs%20to%20be%20harnessed%20in%20a%20way%20that%20their%20precious%20time%20is%20not%20wasted%20while%20looking%20for%20jobs.%20As%20PM%20Modi%20has%20allowed%20for%20%E2%80%98ease%20of%20doing%20business%E2%80%99%20in%20other%20states%2C%20J%26amp%3BK%20should%20also%20be%20taken%20into%20that%20fold%2C%20to%20reduce%20our%20unemployment%20numbers%2C%E2%80%9D%20Tenga%20says.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20April%202023%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cb%3E%2C%20%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cspan%3EJ%26amp%3BK%20held%20the%20third%20spot%20on%20the%20list%20of%20highest%20unemployment%20rates%20in%20India%20at%20an%20alarming%2023.1%25%20.%20This%20marked%20a%20jump%20of%206%25%20from%20March%E2%80%99s%20rate%20of%2017.1%20%25%2C%20as%20per%20the%20Centre%20for%20Monitoring%20Indian%20Economy%20(CMIE).%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20July%202023%2C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cb%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cspan%3Ethe%20unemployment%20rate%20in%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EJ%26amp%3BK%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20stood%20at%2018.3%25%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fjammu-and-kashmir-unemployment-rate-is-a-staggering-18-3-the-national-average-is-4242006%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eaccording%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20to%20MHA%20data%20quoted%20during%20a%20reply%20in%20Rajya%20Sabha.%20The%20national%20unemployment%20average%20stood%20at%20around%208%25%20at%20the%20time.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20unemployment%20numbers%20are%20not%20limited%20to%20the%20number%20of%20people%20living%20without%20livelihood.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAccording%20to%20the%20latest%20data%20from%20the%20National%20Crime%20Records%20Bureau%20(NCRB)%2C%20J%26amp%3BK%20had%20the%20highest%20number%20of%20attempted%20suicides%20in%202022.%20Out%20of%20the%201%2C769%20suicide%20cases%20recorded%20by%20the%20NCRB%20across%20India%20in%202022%2C%20the%20UT%20saw%20497%20deaths%20by%20suicide.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20December%205%2C%202023%2C%20the%20MHA%20said%20that%20around%2078%20persons%20committed%20suicide%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20between%202020%20to%202022%20due%20to%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.greaterkashmir.com%2Fkashmir%2Funemployment-forced-78-persons-to-commit-suicide-in-jk-in-2-years-mha%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eunemployment%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20is%20also%20noteworthy%20that%20the%20NCRB%20report%20states%20that%20since%20the%20reading%20down%20of%20Article%20370%20in%202019%2C%20the%20UT%20saw%20at%20least%20450%20cases%20of%20suicide%2C%20this%20number%20further%20worsened%20in%202021%20with%20the%20toll%20sitting%20at%20586%20cases.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20replying%20to%20a%20query%20raised%20by%20MP%20Vijayakumar%20who%20had%20asked%20whether%20the%20issue%20of%20unemployment%20was%20the%20main%20cause%20of%20youth%20dying%20by%20suicide%20in%20the%20country%2C%20the%20Minister%20of%20State%20in%20the%20MHA%2C%20Nityanand%20Rai%2C%20said%20that%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eofficial%20statistics%20revealed%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Ethat%204%2C88%2C009%20suicides%20%E2%80%93%201%2C53%2C052%20in%202020%2C%201%2C64%2C033%20in%202021%2C%20and%201%2C70%2C924%20in%202022%20were%20reported%20throughout%20the%20country%20from%202020%20to%202022.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20J%26amp%3BK%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E78%20suicides%20including%2046%20in%202020%2C%2015%20in%202021%20and%2017%20in%202022%20were%20reported%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.greaterkashmir.com%2Fkashmir%2Funemployment-forced-78-persons-to-commit-suicide-in-jk-in-2-years-mha%2F%5C%22%3Eowing%20to%20unemployment%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710847819000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F01%2F28134446%2F3891925784_eb02c9d8e3_o.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flabour%2Floans-exams-waiting-tables-jk-youth-say-their-futures-negate-their-education%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Due%20to%20the%20absence%20of%20a%20robust%20private%20sector%20or%20corporate%20culture%2C%20several%20educated%20individuals%20in%20the%20region%20are%20either%20unemployed%20or%20desperately%20trying%20to%20crack%20government%20job%20exams.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flabour%2Floans-exams-waiting-tables-jk-youth-say-their-futures-negate-their-education%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Russian%20mining%20accident%20traps%2013%20as%20Kremlin%20pledges%20full%20rescue%20effort%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710846996000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-108618826%2Cimgsize-1214668.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Frussian-mining-accident-traps-13-as-kremlin-pledges-full-rescue-effort%2Farticleshow%2F108618631.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F108618631.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3E%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Frussian-mining-accident-traps-13-as-kremlin-pledges-full-rescue-effort%2Farticleshow%2F108618631.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia-indiatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Frussian-mining-accident-traps-13-as-kremlin-pledges-full-rescue-effort%2Famp_articleshow%2F108618631.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Frussian-mining-accident-traps-13-as-kremlin-pledges-full-rescue-effort%2Famp_articleshow%2F108618631.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Ahead%20of%20Landmark%20Elections%2C%20Union%20Government%20Silences%20Dissent%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F04%2F04112925%2FVoting_machine_in_India.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EWeeks%20before%20the%20official%20launch%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ffreedomhouse.org%2Freport%2Felection-watch-digital-age%23india-2024%5C%22%3E2024%20general%20election%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0campaign%2C%20the%20leaders%20of%20the%20Indian%20National%20Congress%2C%20currently%20the%20largest%20opposition%20party%2C%20convened%20an%20unusual%20press%20conference.%20They%20announced%20that%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20accounts%20had%20been%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.aljazeera.com%2Fnews%2F2024%2F2%2F16%2Findias-congress-says-25m-funds-frozen-by-tax-department-ahead-of-election%5C%22%3Efrozen%20by%20tax%20authorities%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0over%20a%20payment%20dispute%2C%20locking%20away%20some%202.1%20billion%20rupees%20(%2425.3%20million).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20move%20is%20just%20one%20indicator%20of%20a%20concerning%20trend%3A%20the%20government%20has%20used%20arcane%20regulatory%20enforcement%20actions%20to%20close%20the%20space%20for%20dissent%20across%20the%20country.%20Indians%20who%20criticize%20the%20government%20face%20significant%20risks%2C%20raising%20doubts%20about%20the%20fairness%20of%20the%20upcoming%20elections.%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20who%20leads%20the%20Hindu%20nationalist%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%2C%20is%20running%20for%20a%20third%20five-year%20term%20against%20a%20host%20of%20opposition%20groups.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EGrowing%20obstacles%20to%20government%20criticism%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThough%20Congress%20party%20officials%20will%20reportedly%20retain%20partial%20access%20to%20their%20frozen%20accounts%20until%20the%20dispute%20is%20resolved%2C%20the%20case%20was%20only%20the%20latest%20in%20a%20pattern%20of%20actions%20in%20which%20government%20critics%20have%20suffered%20financial%20repercussions%20at%20the%20hands%20of%20state%20authorities.%20Over%20the%20past%20several%20years%2C%20officials%20have%20issued%20a%20raft%20of%20allegations%20of%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livemint.com%2Fpolitics%2Fnews%2Fmore-than-40-more-opposition-mps-including-shashi-tharoor-suspended-from-lok-sabha-report-11702970155166.html%5C%22%3Efinancial%20impropriety%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20sought%20to%20raid%20or%20restrict%20the%20activities%20of%20opposition%20leaders%2C%20civil%20society%20organisations%2C%20and%20human%20rights%20activists.%20Though%20some%20investigations%20may%20be%20legitimate%20anticorruption%20inquiries%2C%20many%20appear%20to%20be%20politicised.%20In%20effect%2C%20they%20raise%20the%20costs%20for%20criticism%20of%20the%20government%2C%20draining%20the%20resources%20of%20an%20already%20fragile%20civil%20society%20sector%20and%20undermining%20the%20diversity%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20political%20discourse.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndian%20civil%20society%20organisations%20face%20significant%20operational%20barriers%2C%20including%20tight%20restrictions%20on%20foreign%20funding%20under%20the%20Foreign%20Contribution%20Regulation%20Act%20(FCRA).%20To%20fundraise%20internationally%2C%20nonprofits%20must%20be%20licensed%20under%20the%20act%2C%20which%20entails%20strict%20controls%20administered%20by%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Home%20Affairs.%20Authorities%20have%20invoked%20the%20FCRA%20to%20investigate%20prominent%20organizations%20that%20have%20reported%20critically%20on%20the%20government%2C%20including%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Famnesty-fcra-violations-cbi-files-supplementary-charge-sheet%2Farticle67657397.ece%5C%22%3EAmnesty%20International%20India%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20has%20halted%20its%20activities%20because%20of%20the%20probe.%20The%20International%20Commission%20of%20Jurists%20found%20that%20some%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.icj.org%2Findia-repressive-law-on-foreign-contributions-stifles-ngos-must-be-revised-or-scrapped%2F%5C%22%3E19%2C000%20FCRA%20licenses%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0were%20canceled%20between%202014%20and%202020%2C%20noting%20that%20the%20cancellations%20were%20imposed%20%E2%80%9Cselectively%20to%20silence%20critical%20voices.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndividuals%20involved%20in%20civil%20society%20activism%20are%20not%20much%20safer.%20Prominent%20journalist%20Rana%20Ayyub%2C%20one%20of%20the%20most%20vocal%20critics%20of%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20Hindu%20nationalist%20agenda%2C%20has%20endured%20multiple%20rounds%20of%20legal%20and%20extralegal%20harassment%2C%20including%20a%20years-long%20money-laundering%20investigation%20over%20the%20alleged%20misappropriation%20of%20funds%20from%20a%20COVID-19%20relief%20effort.%20BJP%20critic%20Harsh%20Mander%2C%20formerly%20affiliated%20with%20the%20Congress%20party%2C%20has%20seen%20his%20home%20raided%20and%20his%20nonprofit%20investigated%20over%20alleged%20FCRA%20violations%2C%20with%20fellow%20activists%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fvindictive-witch-hunt-over-250-condemn-raids-on-harsh-mander%5C%22%3Edenouncing%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0the%20enforcement%20actions%20as%20politically%20motivated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20sprawling%20censorship%20apparatus%20to%20limit%20information%20diversity%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%E2%80%99s%202024%20elections%20will%20be%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20largest%2C%20with%20over%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wionews.com%2Findia-news%2Fgeneral-elections-2024-9688-crore-people-registered-to-vote-for-polls-election-commission-688693%5C%22%3E986%20million%20people%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0registered%20to%20vote.%20Hundreds%20of%20millions%20of%20citizens%20will%20rely%20on%20the%20internet%20to%20learn%20about%20the%20candidates%20and%20party%20platforms.%20But%20the%20Indian%20government%20has%20asserted%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ffreedomhouse.org%2Fcountry%2Findia%2Ffreedom-net%2F2023%5C%22%3Eincreasing%20authority%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0over%20online%20content%2C%20particularly%20under%20the%20BJP%2C%20and%20it%20regularly%20forces%20social%20media%20companies%20to%20remove%20content%20that%20officials%20deem%20unlawful.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECritics%20of%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%2C%20the%20ruling%20party%2C%20or%20the%20Hindu%20nationalist%20policies%20that%20they%20champion%20are%20the%20prime%20targets%20of%20this%20censorship%20apparatus.%20In%20the%20first%20two%20months%20of%202024%2C%20the%20websites%20and%20social%20media%20accounts%20and%20posts%20that%20Indian%20authorities%20sought%20to%20scrub%20from%20the%20internet%20included%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3Ea%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fmedia%2Funion-govt-uses-it-act-to-attack-press-freedom-asks-caravan-to-take-down-report%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ECaravan%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3Emagazine%20article%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0alleging%20that%20Indian%20soldiers%20killed%20three%20civilians%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3Eover%20a%20dozen%20social%20media%20accounts%20linked%20to%20the%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fscroll.in%2Flatest%2F1063714%2Famid-farmers-protests-over-a-dozen-social-media-accounts-withheld-in-india%5C%22%3Eleaders%20of%20a%20farmers%E2%80%99%20protest%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20who%20called%20for%20a%20stronger%20social%20safety%20net%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3Ea%20post%20on%20X%20(formerly%20Twitter)%20from%20the%20US-based%20Sikh%20Coalition%2C%20calling%20on%20President%20Joseph%20Biden%20to%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sikhcoalition.org%2Fpress-release%2Fsikh-coalition-statement-on-notice-of-withholding-from-x-and-indian-government-censorship%2F%5C%22%3Eadvocate%20for%20the%20rights%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0of%20the%20protesting%20farmers%3B%20and%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EHindutva%20Watch%20and%20India%20Hate%20Lab%2C%20two%20websites%20dedicated%20to%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.aljazeera.com%2Fnews%2F2024%2F1%2F31%2Fhate-crime-tracker-hindutva-watch-blocked-in-india-ahead-of-national-vote%5C%22%3Etracking%20hate%20crimes%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0and%20hate%20speech%20in%20India%2C%20as%20well%20as%20some%20affiliated%20social%20media%20accounts.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20affected%20content%20ranged%20from%20independent%20civil%20society%20research%20that%20reflected%20unfavorably%20on%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20policies%20to%20online%20civic%20mobilisation%20that%20sought%20to%20influence%20policy%20directly.%20Diverse%20and%20independent%20discussion%20of%20politics%2C%20the%20economy%2C%20and%20broader%20societal%20challenges%20plays%20a%20critical%20role%20in%20shaping%20voters%E2%80%99%20choices%20ahead%20of%20elections.%20Degrading%20access%20to%20such%20information%20fundamentally%20limits%20free%20decision-making%20and%20infringes%20on%20the%20exercise%20of%20citizens%E2%80%99%20most%20important%20political%20right.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAn%20uneven%20playing%20field%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20free%20and%20fair%20election%20requires%20an%20environment%20in%20which%20people%20can%20discuss%20politics%2C%20express%20their%20personal%20views%2C%20and%20access%20information%20about%20the%20government%20and%20opposition%20without%20fear%20of%20retribution.%20From%20politicised%20FCRA%20enforcement%20to%20partisan%20online%20censorship%2C%20the%20Indian%20government%E2%80%99s%20actions%20have%20undermined%20these%20basic%20rights.%20They%20also%20underscore%20officials%E2%80%99%20willingness%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ffreedomhouse.org%2Freport%2Ffreedom-world%2F2024%2Fmounting-damage-flawed-elections-and-armed-conflict%23manipulating-elections-undermining-democracy%5C%22%3Edeploy%20state%20resources%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20influence%20the%20elections%20in%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20favour.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGovernment%20officials%E2%80%94including%20the%20tax%20investigation%20authorities%20at%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Finance%20and%20those%20at%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Electronics%20and%20Information%20Technology%20who%20are%20tasked%20with%20enforcing%20online%20content%20regulations%E2%80%94should%20ensure%20that%20law%20enforcement%20efforts%20do%20not%20harm%20the%20conduct%20of%20the%20elections.%20Investigations%20into%20alleged%20FCRA%20irregularities%20should%20not%20be%20initiated%20for%20political%20purposes%2C%20whether%20to%20hinder%20opposition%20politicians%20or%20to%20limit%20the%20activities%20of%20a%20civil%20society%20group.%20Independent%20oversight%20is%20crucial%3A%20election%20authorities%20should%20vigorously%20apply%20the%20principles%20set%20out%20in%20the%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fweb.archive.org%2Fweb%2F20140407100248%2Fhttp%3A%2Feci.nic.in%2Feci_main%2FMCC-ENGLISH_28022014.pdf%5C%22%3EModel%20Code%20of%20Conduct%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20takes%20effect%20when%20election%20dates%20are%20announced%20and%20calls%20on%20the%20ruling%20party%20to%20not%20abuse%20%E2%80%9Cits%20official%20position%20for%20the%20purposes%20of%20its%20election%20campaign.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThose%20corrective%20measures%20alone%20will%20not%20guarantee%20free%20and%20fair%20elections.%20Political%20leaders%20have%20employed%20even%20blunter%20instruments%20to%20silence%20dissent.%20Indian%20journalists%20are%20all%20too%20frequently%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ffreedomhouse.org%2Fcountry%2Findia%2Ffreedom-net%2F2023%5C%22%3Earrested%20or%20prosecuted%3C%2Fa%3E%20over%20critical%20reporting%2C%20opposition%20politicians%20have%20been%20disqualified%20from%20running%20or%20barred%20from%20the%20legislature%2C%20and%20internet%20shutdowns%20remain%20common.%20However%2C%20a%20truly%20democratic%20process%20will%20be%20impossible%20if%20free%20expression%20is%20not%20protected%20from%20politicised%2C%20disproportionate%2C%20and%20illegitimate%20interference%20by%20government%20actors.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EKian%20Vesteinsson%20is%20Senior%20Research%20Analyst%2C%20Technology%20and%20Democracy.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20article%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ffreedomhouse.org%2Farticle%2Fahead-landmark-elections-indias-government-silences-dissent%5C%22%3Eoriginally%20published%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20the%20Freedom%20House%20website.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710846052000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F04%2F04112925%2FVoting_machine_in_India.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fahead-of-landmark-elections-union-government-silences-dissent%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20ruling%20party%20has%20deployed%20state%20regulators%20against%20its%20critics.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fahead-of-landmark-elections-union-government-silences-dissent%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22By%20Dismissing%20Doubts%20Over%20EVMs%2C%20EC%20Must%20Know%20It%20Can't%20Promise%20a%20Free%20and%20Fair%20Elections%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F10211621%2FEffect-2024-02-10T202212.238.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20announcing%20the%20schedule%20for%20the%2018th%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20on%20March%2016%2C%20Chief%20Election%20Commissioner%20(CEC)%20Rajiv%20Kumar%20snubbed%20the%20Doubting%20Thomases%20who%20question%20the%20reliability%20of%20EVMs%20(which%20most%20of%20the%20electorate%20do).%20He%20was%20at%20his%20poetic%20best%20and%20hit%20out%20at%20EVM%20doubters%20by%20sharing%20an%20Urdu%20couplet%20he%20had%20penned%20on%20how%20the%20machines%20would%20have%20themselves%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsundayguardianlive.com%2Fnews%2Fcec-snubs-those-doubting-evms%5C%22%3Eresponded%20to%20such%20allegations.%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CAdhooree%20hasaraton%20ka%20iljaam%20har%20baar%20ham%20par%20lagana%20theek%20nahin%2C%20vafa%20khud%20se%20nahin%20hoti%2C%20khata%20EVM%20ki%20kahate%20ho%3C%2Fem%3E%20(It%20is%20not%20right%20to%20blame%20us%20every%20time%20for%20unfulfilled%20desires.%20While%20you%20fail%20to%20prove%20yourself%2C%20you%20say%20it%20is%20the%20fault%20of%20EVM).%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECEC%20mocked%20democratic%20voices%20when%20he%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fvideos%2Ftoi-original%2Fchief-election-commissioner-rajiv-kumar-mocks-social-media-evm-experts-amid-laughs%2Fvideoshow%2F108548564.cms%5C%22%3Ederided%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20political%20parties%2C%20social%20media%20and%20EVM%20experts%20demanding%20the%20banning%20of%20EVMs%20amid%20laughs%20saying%20that%20the%20machines%20made%20the%20poll%20process%20fairer%20and%20better%20and%20expressed%20his%20expert%20opinion%20that%20all%20parties%20know%20this%20in%20their%20hearts.%20And%20he%20falsely%20claimed%20that%20courts%20have%20certified%20the%20integrity%20of%20these%20machines.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fare-indias-elections-free-and-fair%5C%22%3EAre%20India%E2%80%99s%20Elections%20Free%20and%20Fair%3F%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20utterances%20expose%20CEC%E2%80%99s%20ignorance%20of%20the%20basic%20concept%20of%20elections%20and%20democracy.%20His%20comment%20that%20only%20those%20who%20lose%20elections%20question%20the%20reliability%20of%20EVMs%20implies%20that%20elections%20are%20only%20meant%20for%20political%20parties%20and%20the%20candidates%2C%20which%20is%20a%20fallacy.%20He%20should%20know%20that%20in%20a%20democracy%20sovereignty%20vests%20with%20the%20citizens%20and%20elections%20are%20the%20tool%20for%20the%20citizens%20to%20transfer%20this%20sovereignty%20to%20his%2Fher%20chosen%20representative%20once%20in%20five%20years.%20To%20do%20so%20elections%20and%20voting%20system%20must%20adhere%20to%20certain%20%E2%80%9Cdemocratic%20principles%E2%80%9D%20which%20are%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Col%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20voting%20process%20should%20be%20transparent%20in%20a%20manner%20that%20the%20general%20public%20can%20be%20satisfied%20that%20their%20vote%20is%20correctly%20recorded%20and%20counted.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20voting%20and%20counting%20process%20should%20be%20publicly%20auditable.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EOrdinary%20citizens%20should%20be%20able%20to%20check%20the%20essential%20steps%20in%20the%20voting%20process.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThere%20should%20be%20verifiability%20in%20the%20counting%20of%20votes%20and%20ascertainment%20of%20the%20results%20reliably%20without%20too%20much%20special%20knowledge.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20election%20process%20should%20be%20free%20and%20fair%2C%20and%20also%20be%20seen%20to%20be%20free%20and%20fair.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20Election%20Commission%20should%20be%20in%20full%20control%20of%20the%20entire%20voting%20process%2C%20and%20the%20public%20at%20large%20should%20be%20able%20to%20verify%20the%20casting%20and%20counting%20of%20their%20votes.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EElectronic%20processes%20and%20technological%20practices%20should%20be%20subject%20to%20public%20scrutiny%2Fexaminability.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20short%2C%20the%20voting%2Fcounting%20system%20must%20ensure%20that%20the%20voter%20should%20have%20the%20knowledge%20that%20her%20vote%20is%20cast%20as%20intended%2C%20recorded%20as%20cast%20and%20counted%20as%20recorded.%20Why%20has%20not%20the%20CEC%20ever%20responded%20to%20this%20critical%20poser%20raised%20by%20several%20sources%20including%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fconstitutionalconduct.files.wordpress.com%2F2021%2F04%2Fcitizens-commission-on-elections-vol.-i.pdf%5C%22%3EReport%20of%20the%20Citizens%20Commission%20on%20Elections%20(CCE)%3C%2Fa%3E%20headed%20by%20a%20former%20Supreme%20Court%20judge%20which%20was%20submitted%20to%20the%20ECI%20in%20January%2FFebruary%202021%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%20to%20the%20CEC%E2%80%99s%20half-baked%20poetry%2C%20%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20not%20right%20to%20blame%20us%20every%20time%20for%20unfulfilled%20desires.%20While%20you%20fail%20to%20prove%20yourself%2C%20you%20say%20it%20is%20the%20fault%20of%20EVM.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDid%20the%20CEC%20go%20through%20the%20report%20of%20the%20CCE%2C%20the%20expert%20group%20which%20had%20reviewed%20the%20functioning%20of%20EVMs%20primarily%20on%20the%20touchstone%20of%20whether%20and%20how%20far%20their%20use%20complied%20with%20the%20%E2%80%98democracy%20principles.%E2%80%99%20In%20short%2C%20it%20insists%20on%20absolute%20transparency%20in%20facilitating%20the%20voter%20to%20exercise%20his%20or%20her%20choice%20and%20in%20ensuring%20that%20these%20selections%20are%2C%20indeed%2C%20reflected%20in%20the%20stored%20vote%20and%20counted%20as%20such%E2%80%94%20without%20the%20slightest%20deviation%20whatsoever.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F08202025%2FUntitled-design-36.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F08202025%2FUntitled-design-36.png%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F08202025%2FUntitled-design-36-300x140.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F08202025%2FUntitled-design-36-1024x478.png%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-700860%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ERepresentational%20image.%20Voters%20at%20a%20polling%20booth%20in%20Bangalore%20during%202009%20general%20elections.%20Photo%3A%20Wikimedia%20Commons%2FRanjit%20Bhaskar%2FCC%20BY-SA%202.0%20DEED%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20principles%20also%20mandate%20that%20the%20voting%20procedure%20is%20easily%20understandable%20and%20verifiable%20by%20the%20voter%20and%20open%20to%20audit%20without%20complications%20even%20when%20relevant%20technology%20is%20utilised.%20There%20should%20be%20absolutely%20no%20scope%20for%20error%20or%20misrepresentation%20of%20the%20elector%E2%80%99s%20choice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECCE%20had%20relied%20on%20depositions%20and%20opinions%20of%20several%20national%20and%20international%20experts%20and%20was%20informed%20of%20the%20reasons%20why%20even%20the%20most%20advanced%20countries%20do%20not%20prefer%20the%20use%20of%20EVMs%20during%20polls.%20Among%20the%20domain%20knowledge%20holders%20who%20submitted%20deposition%20before%20this%20CCE%20group%20were%20Ronald%20L.%20Rivest%20of%20the%20Massachusetts%20Institute%20of%20Technology%2C%20Cambridge%2C%20USA%3B%20Alex%20Halderman%20of%20the%20University%20of%20Michigan%2C%20USA%3B%20Poorvi%20L.%20Vora%20and%20Bhagirath%20Narahari%20of%20George%20Washington%20University%2C%20USA%3B%20Alok%20Choudhary%20of%20North-western%20University%2C%20USA%20Sandeep%20Shukla%2C%20Professor%2C%20Computer%20Science%20and%20Engineering%2C%20IIT%20Kanpur%3B%20Douglas%20W.%20Jones%20of%20the%20University%20of%20Iowa%2C%20USA%3B%20Nasir%20Memon%20of%20New%20York%20University%20(Brooklyn)%2C%20USA%3B%20Philip%20B.%20Stark%20of%20the%20University%20of%20California%2C%20Berkeley%2C%20Vanessa%20Teague%2C%20Associate%20Professor%2C%20School%20of%20Computing%20and%20Information%20Systems%2C%20University%20of%20Melbourne%2C%20Cybersecurity%2C%20Australia%3B%20Bappa%20Sinha%20of%20Free%20Software%20Movement%20of%20India%2C%20Subodh%20Sharma%20of%20Computer%20Science%20and%20Engineering%20and%20of%20the%20School%20of%20Public%20Policy%2C%20IIT%2C%20Delhi%3B%20KV%20Subrahmanyam%2C%20Professor%2C%20Computer%20Science%2C%20Chennai%20Mathematical%20Institute%2C%20Chennai%3B%20Dr%20Sanjiva%20Prasad%20and%20Dr.%20Subhashis%20Banerjee%20of%20IIT%2C%20Delhi%20and%20Anupam%20Saraf%2C%20Professor%20and%20Future%20Designer%20among%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20are%20the%20best%20brains%20on%20the%20subject%20across%20the%20globe%20and%20it%20would%20not%20be%20possible%20to%20put%20together%20another%20group%20to%20match%20this%20vast%20and%20varied%20expertise.%20And%20the%20conclusions%20of%20the%20CCE%20report%20are%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Col%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EDue%20to%20the%20absence%20of%20End-to-End%20(E2E)%20verifiability%2C%20the%20present%20EVM%2FVVAPAT%20system%20is%20not%20verifiable%20and%20therefore%20is%20unfit%20for%20democratic%20elections.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThat%20an%20EVM%20has%20not%20yet%20been%20detected%20to%20have%20been%20hacked%20provides%20no%20guarantee%20that%20it%20cannot%20be%20hacked.%20Thus%2C%20elections%20must%20be%20conducted%20assuming%20that%20the%20EVMs%20may%20possibly%20be%20tampered%20with.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EIn%20practice%2C%20it%20may%20be%20necessary%20to%20test%20more%20EVMs%20than%20even%20what%20the%20civil%20society%20and%20the%20political%20parties%20demand%20(30%25%20and%2050%25%20respectively)%20to%20ensure%20verification%20and%20reliable%20ascertainment%20of%20results.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThere%20must%20be%20stringent%20pre-audit%20of%20the%20electronic%20vote%20count%20before%20the%20results%20are%20declared.%20The%20audit%20may%20in%20some%20cases%20%E2%80%93%20depending%20on%20the%20margin%20of%20victory%20%E2%80%93%20require%20a%20full%20manual%20counting%20of%20VVPAT%20slips.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20electronic%20voting%20system%20should%20be%20re-designed%20to%20be%20software%20and%20hardware%20independent%20in%20order%20to%20be%20verifiable%20or%20auditable.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CEC%20should%20know%20that%20none%20in%20the%20CCE%20or%20those%20who%20deposed%20had%20%E2%80%9Cunfulfilled%20desires%E2%80%9D%20to%20capture%20political%20power%20by%20any%20means%20and%20did%20not%20fault%20the%20EVM%20for%20failing%20to%20do%20so!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fthe-case-for-bringing-paper-ballots-back%5C%22%3EThe%20Case%20for%20Bringing%20Paper%20Ballots%20Back%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3Cins%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIntegrity%20of%20EVMs%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%20to%20the%20falsehood%20about%20the%20courts%20certifying%20the%20integrity%20of%20EVMs.%20The%20first%20serious%20legal%20challenge%20to%20EVMs%20was%20made%20by%20Dr%20Subramanian%20Swamy%20of%20BJP%20in%20the%20Delhi%20high%20vourt%20in%20W.P.(C)%20No.%2011879%20of%202009%20and%20this%20was%20the%20verdict%20in%20January%202012%3A%20%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CDr.%20Swamy%20is%20right%20to%20the%20extent%20that%20it%20cannot%20be%20ruled%20out%20that%20EVMs%20may%20be%20vulnerable%20to%20frauds.%C2%A0%20There%20may%20be%20security%20issues%20as%20well%3C%2Fem%3E.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Swamy%20moved%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20for%20relief.%20On%20October%208%2C%202013%20the%20Court%20confirming%20the%20doubts%20on%20the%20integrity%20of%20EVMs%20mandated%20the%20use%20of%20voter%20verified%20paper%20audit%20trail%20(VVPAT)%20system%20in%20a%20phased%20manner%20to%20bring%20about%20some%20semblance%20of%20democratic%20principles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Court%20observed%3A%20%E2%80%9CFrom%20the%20materials%20placed%20by%20both%20the%20sides%2C%20we%20are%20satisfied%20that%20the%20%E2%80%98paper%20trail%E2%80%99%20is%20an%20indispensable%20requirement%20of%20free%20and%20fair%20elections.%20The%20confidence%20of%20the%20voters%20in%20the%20EVMs%20can%20be%20achieved%20only%20with%20the%20introduction%20of%20the%20%E2%80%98paper%20trail%E2%80%99.%20EVMs%20with%20VVPAT%20system%20ensure%20the%20accuracy%20of%20the%20voting%20system.%20With%20an%20intent%20to%20have%20fullest%20transparency%20in%20the%20system%20and%20to%20restore%20the%20confidence%20of%20the%20voters%2C%20it%20is%20necessary%20to%20set%20up%20EVMs%20with%20VVPAT%20system%20because%20vote%20is%20nothing%20but%20an%20act%20of%20expression%20which%20has%20immense%20importance%20in%20democratic%20system.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20the%20VVPAT%20system%20introduced%20thus%20has%20been%20morphed%20into%20a%20meaningless%20bioscope%20is%20another%20story!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20writer%20himself%20had%20filed%20W.P(C)%201514%20of%202018%20titled%20%3Cem%3EM.G.%20Devasahayam%20%26amp%3B%20Ors.%20v.%20Election%20Commission%20of%20India%3C%2Fem%3E%20in%20which%20vide%20judgement%20reported%20as%20N.%20Chandrababu%20Naidu%20v.%20Union%20of%20India%2C%20(2019)%2015%20SCC%20377%2C%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20keeping%20in%20mind%20that%20the%20ECI%20had%2C%20%E2%80%9Cpointed%20out%20infrastructure%20difficulties%2C%20including%20manpower%20availability%2C%20at%20this%20point%20of%20time%2C%20in%20increasing%20the%20number%20of%20EVMs%20for%20verification%E2%80%9D%20because%20of%20which%20the%2C%20%E2%80%9Cdeclaration%20of%20result%20of%20election%20could%20be%20delayed%20by%205-6%20days%2C%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%20directed%20the%20ECI%20to%20count%20VVPATs%20in%20five%20polling%20stations%20per%20assembly%20constituency%20as%20opposed%20to%20the%20prayer%20in%20the%20writ%20petition%20for%20counting%20of%2030%25%20VVPATs%20across%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Court%20at%20that%20point%20in%20time%20had%20found%20that%2C%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20proximity%20to%20the%20election%20schedule%20announced%20by%20the%20ECI%20must%20be%20kept%20in%20mind.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%20significantly%2C%20vide%20the%20same%20order%2C%20Writ%20Petition%20(C)%20No.%2023%20of%202019%20was%20disposed%20of%20by%20the%20Court%20expressing%20its%20%E2%80%9Creluctance%20to%20go%20into%20the%20issues%20regarding%20the%20integrity%20of%20the%20EVMs%20which%20have%20been%20raised%20at%20a%20belated%20stage.%20The%20petition%20was%20filed%20in%20the%20month%20of%20December%202018%20raising%20various%20technical%20issues%20which%20are%20not%20possible%20to%20be%20gone%20into%20at%20this%20stage.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHow%20can%20a%20CEC%20utter%20such%20falsehood%3F%20As%20an%20ordinary%20citizen%20of%20the%20country%2C%20I%20would%20like%20to%20ask%20the%20CEC%20one%20question.%20As%20it%20is%20because%20of%20the%20totally%20partisan%20way%20in%20which%20CEC%20and%20Election%20Commissioners%20are%20being%20selected%20and%20appointed%20and%20the%20alienation%20of%20the%20Commission%20from%20the%20public%20and%20political%20opposition%2C%20the%20credibility%20of%20ECI%20is%20at%20a%20very%20low%20ebb.%20Why%20is%20he%20lowering%20it%20further%20by%20serenading%20the%20Black-Box%20called%20EVM%20which%20can%20be%20grossly%20misused%20for%20bulk-manufacturing%20of%20votes%20to%20steal%20peoples%E2%80%99%20mandate%3F%C2%A0%20And%20in%20the%20process%20mocking%20the%20people%20who%20seek%20free%20and%20fair%20elections%3F%20Pray%2C%20is%20this%20the%20mandate%20of%20the%20ECI%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710844154000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F10211621%2FEffect-2024-02-10T202212.238.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fby-dismissing-doubts-over-evms-ec-must-know-it-cant-promise-a-free-and-fair-elections%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20recent%20snub%20against%20EVM%20doubters%20by%20chief%20election%20commissioner%20that%20it%20is%20'wrong%20to%20blame%20EVMs%20for%20your%20unfulfilled%20desires'%20expose%20CEC%E2%80%99s%20ignorance%20of%20the%20basic%20concept%20of%20elections%20and%20democracy.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fby-dismissing-doubts-over-evms-ec-must-know-it-cant-promise-a-free-and-fair-elections%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%E2%80%98I%20Save%20600%20Litres%20of%20Water%20Everyday%E2%80%99%3A%20Bengaluru%20Doctor%20Shares%20Easy%20Tricks%20To%20Start%20At%20Home%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EFeatured%20image%20(R)%20courtesy%3A%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fdivya_sharmaMD%2Fstatus%2F1510273297186918403%2Fphoto%2F1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDr%20Divya%20Sharma%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Bengaluru%2C%20where%20water%20shortages%20are%20becoming%20a%20big%20problem%2C%20people%20are%20coming%20up%20with%20clever%20ways%20to%20deal%20with%20it.%20Some%20are%20taking%20shorter%20showers%2C%20while%20others%20are%20working%20from%20home%20to%20save%20water.%20Some%20are%20even%20using%20public%20toilets%20more%20and%20looking%20into%20ways%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2Fweb-stories%2Fbengaluru-water-crises-how-the-greens-society-is-saving-water-and-reducing-water-bills%2F%5C%22%