%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERest%20The%20Case%20provides%20legal%20information%2C%20from%20basic%20templates%20to%20bare%20acts%2C%20legal%20drafting%2C%20and%20a%20list%20of%20lawyers.%20It%20has%20also%20created%20a%20network%20base%20for%20lawyers%20of%20different%20specialisations%20to%20connect%20with%20clients.%20More%20than%201%2C200%20lawyers%20from%20across%20the%20country%20are%20already%20a%20part%20of%20it.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Shreya%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20charge%20anything%20from%20clients%2C%20she%20has%20created%20different%20packages%20for%20lawyers%2C%20making%20a%20revenue%20of%20Rs%201.25%20crores%20in%20the%202022-23%20financial%20year%20alone.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20aim%2C%20she%20shares%20with%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20is%20to%20provide%20the%20right%20legal%20information%20with%20just%20a%20click.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ESimplifying%20legal%20jargon%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201600px)%20100vw%2C%201600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Frest-the-case-3-min-1710763667.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221600%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Shreya%20Sharma%20started%20Rest%20The%20Case%20in%202021%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Frest-the-case-3-min-1710763667.jpeg%201600w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Frest-the-case-3-min-1710763667-300x225.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Frest-the-case-3-min-1710763667-500x375.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Frest-the-case-3-min-1710763667-768x576.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Frest-the-case-3-min-1710763667-1536x1152.jpeg%201536w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetter