%20but%20ultimately%20chose%20aquaponics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20major%20difference%20between%20hydroponic%20and%20aquaponic%20setup%20is%20the%20media%20used%20to%20provide%20nutrients%20to%20the%20soil.%20It%20has%20a%20similar%20setup%20of%20hydroponics%20but%20with%20an%20additional%20fish%20tank%20to%20breed%20fish.%20The%20fish%20excreta%20is%20decomposed%20by%20bacteria%20into%20nitrate%20which%20is%20an%20ideal%20fertiliser%20for%20plants.%20It%20is%20like%20imitating%20the%20river%20ecology.%20Through%20this%20fish%20tank%2C%20water%20is%20regulated%20throughout%20small%20tanks%20that%20hold%20plants%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Shashank.%20He%20upcycled%20drums%20and%20cans%20to%20use%20as%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F82739%2Fifarm-integrated-aquaponics-poultry-kerala-veterinary-university%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20fish%20tanks.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBesides%20nitrates%20produced%20by%20fish%20waste%2C%20he%20also%20adds%20iron%20nails%2C%20lime%20and%20egg%20shells%20to%20increase%20the%20iron%20and%20calcium%20nutrients.%20After%20six%20months%20of%20research%20and%20assistance%20from%20ICAR-CAFRI%2C%20he%20successfully%20grew%20vegetables%20in%20a%20600%20sq%20ft%20area%20for%20three%20years.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202018%2C%20he%20decided%20to%20quit%20his%20job%20and%20grow%20vegetables%20in%20a%20commercial%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F343071%2Fhow-to-grow-strawberries-dragon-fruit-turmeric-terrace-gardening%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eterrace%20setup.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPresently%2C%20he%20grows%20nearly%202%2C500%20varieties%20of%20plants%2C%20which%20include%20green%20leafy%20vegetables%2C%20medicinal%20herbs%2C%20and%20flowers%20and%20harvests%20500%20kg%20of%20vegetables%20every%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22