ue%20to%20drive%20change%20in%20rural%20areas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHeld%20from%2015%20to%2019%20November%20each%20year%2C%20Samvaad%20honours%20the%20legacy%20of%20Birsa%20Munda%20%E2%80%94%20a%20tribal%20independence%20activist%20and%20leader%20from%20Jharkhand%E2%80%99s%20Munda%20tribe.%20In%20its%20tenth%20year%2C%20themed%20%E2%80%98Walk%20with%20Me%E2%80%99%2C%20Samvaad%20reflected%20on%20a%20decade%20of%20impactful%20dialogues%2C%20recognising%20the%20journey%20of%20ideas%20and%20changemakers%20shaping%20the%20present%20and%20future.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20different%20elements%20of%20Samvaad%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F161926%2Fandhra-pradesh-araku-coffee-gold-paris-news%2F%5C%22%3Eincluding%20f%3C%2Fa%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F161926%2Fandhra-pradesh-araku-coffee-gold-paris-news%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eo%3C%2Fa%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F161926%2Fandhra-pradesh-araku-coffee-gold-paris-news%2F%5C%22%3Eod%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20music%2C%20artisans%2C%20cultural%20markers%2C%20and%20others%2C%20bring%20a%20lot%20of%20intangible%20potential%20through%20this%20tribal%20cultural%20conclave.%20It%20is%20not%20only%20a%20platform%20of%20expression%20but%20also%20a%20forum%20for%20meaningful%20dialogues%20that%20add%20perspectives%20to%20the%20different%20aspects%20of%20life%20and%20one%E2%80%99s%20journey%20through%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Sourav%20Roy%2C%20CEO%20of%20TSF.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20continued%2C%20%E2%80%9CThroughout%20the%20year%2C%20we%20engage%20with%20the%20tribes%20through%20our%20initiatives%20to%20converge%20on%20dialogues%20that%20set%20the%20tone%20for%20Samvaad%20each%20year.%20Many%20new%20ideas%20and%20innovations%20emerge%20from%20these%20conversations%2C%20moderated%20by%20experts%20from%20respective%20fields%20and%20changemakers%20from%20all%20over%20the%20country.%20Cele